0and%20chose%20to%20enact%20industry-standard%20guardrails%20that%20would%20prevent%20the%20use%20of%20their%20products%20by%20one%20extremely%20dangerous%20group%3A%20child%20sex%20predators.%20XAI%20did%20not%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERepresentatives%20for%20Musk%20and%20xAI%20did%20not%20immediately%20respond%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment%20by%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMusk%20previously%20said%20in%20a%20January%20post%20on%20X%20that%20he%20was%20%26quot%3Bnot%20aware%20of%20any%20naked%20underage%20images%20generated%20by%20Grok.%20Literally%20zero.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGrok%20generates%20images%20based%20on%20user%20prompts%2C%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20asked%20to%20generate%20images%2C%20it%20will%20refuse%20to%20produce%20anything%20illegal%2C%20as%20the%20operating%20principle%20for%20Grok%20is%20to%20obey%20the%20laws%20of%20any%20given%20country%20or%20state%2C%26quot%3B%20Musk%20said.%20%26quot%3BThere%20may%20be%20times%20when%20adversarial%20hacking%20of%20Grok%20prompts%20does%20something%20unexpected.%20If%20that%20happens%2C%20we%20fix%20the%20bug%20immediately.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20against%20xAI%20says%20that%20the%20Tennessee%20plaintiffs%20are%20%26quot%3Bthree%20of%20the%20minor%20victims%20of%20xAI's%20knowing%20production%2C%20possession%2C%20and%20distribution%20of%20AI-generated%20child%20sexual%20abuse%20material%26quot%3B%20depicting%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20plaintiffs%2C%20identified%20in%20the%20court%20papers%20only%20as%20Jane%20Doe%201%2C%20Jane%20Doe%202%2C%20and%20Jane%20Doe%203%2C%20allege%20that%20xAI's%20AI%20tools%20were%20used%20to%20make%20nude%20images%20and%20videos%20of%20them.%20Jane%20Doe%201%2C%20a%20recent%20adult%2C%20was%20a%20minor%20at%20the%20time%20of%20the%20alleged%20incidents%2C%20while%20the%20two%20other%20plaintiffs%20are%20still%20minors%2C%20according%20to%20the%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20December%202025%2C%20Jane%20Doe%201%20received%20a%20message%20from%20an%20anonymous%20Instagram%20account%20warning%20her%20that%20%26quot%3Bpics%26quot%3B%20of%20her%20had%20been%20generated%20by%20someone%20she%20knew%20and%20spread%20across%20the%20group-chat%20platform%20Discord.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThrough%20a%20series%20of%20messages%2C%20the%20anonymous%20user%20went%20on%20to%20explain%20that%20the%20perpetrator%20had%20uploaded%20a%20folder%20of%20image%20and%20video%20files%20depicting%20her%20and%20other%20minor%20females%20to%20Discord%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20anonymous%20user%20eventually%20sent%20Jane%20Doe%201%20several%20sexualized%20AI-generated%20images%20and%20videos%20of%20her%20and%20other%20minor%20girls%2C%20according%20to%20the%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAt%20least%20five%20of%20these%20files%2C%20one%20video%20and%20four%20images%2C%20depicted%20her%20actual%20face%20and%20body%20in%20settings%20with%20which%20she%20was%20familiar%2C%20but%20morphed%20into%20sexually%20explicit%20poses%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20says.%20%26quot%3BThe%20images%20showed%20her%20entire%20body%2C%20including%20her%20genitals%2C%20without%20any%20clothes.%20The%20video%20depicted%20her%20undressing%20until%20she%20was%20entirely%20nude.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJane%20Doe%201%20alerted%20the%20other%20minors%20in%20the%20images%20and%20their%20families%2C%20and%20a%20criminal%20investigation%20was%20opened%20in%20Tennessee%2C%20according%20to%20the%20lawsuit.%20It%20added%20that%20local%20police%20arrested%20a%20suspect%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20case%20in%20December%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20month%2C%20Jane%20Doe%202%20learned%20through%20the%20investigation%20that%20at%20least%20two%20of%20her%20images%20had%20also%20been%20used%20to%20produce%20sexually%20explicit%20AI-generated%20content%20using%20xAI's%20tools%2C%20the%20lawsuit%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELocal%20law%20enforcement%20told%20the%20girl%20and%20her%20mother%20that%20one%20image%20taken%20of%20the%20girl%20on%20the%20beach%20in%20a%20blue%20bikini%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bmorphed%20to%20depict%20her%20without%20any%20clothes%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20lawsuit%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAuthorities%20also%20informed%20Jane%20Doe%203%20that%20the%20AI-generated%20images%20recovered%20from%20the%20suspect's%20phone%20included%20one%20that%20had%20been%20%26quot%3Bmorphed%20to%20depict%20her%20fully%20nude%2C%26quot%3B%20according%20to%20the%20lawsuit.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVanessa%20Baehr-Jones%2C%20an%20attorney%20for%20the%20plaintiffs%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20her%20clients%20have%20endured%20a%20%26quot%3Bnightmare.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTheir%20CSAM%20images%20and%20videos%20depicting%20them%20when%20they%20were%20minors%20are%20now%20forever%20out%20there%20on%20the%20internet%20in%20these%20dark%20net%20worlds%20of%20child%20sex%20predators%2C%26quot%3B%20Baehr-Jones%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20harm%20from%20that%20is%20acute.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20attorney%20said%20she%20hopes%20the%20lawsuit%20brings%20%26quot%3Baccountability%26quot%3B%20for%20xAI%20and%20that%20%26quot%3Bmost%20importantly%2C%20this%20should%20never%20happen%20to%20any%20other%20victim.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20lawsuit%20seeks%20unspecified%20damages%20and%20accuses%20xAI%20of%20production%20with%20the%20intent%20to%20distribute%20child%20pornography%2C%20distribution%20of%20child%20pornography%2C%20and%20possession%20of%20child%20pornography%2C%20among%20other%20claims.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20our%20legal%20system%2C%20money%20is%20the%20way%20we%20make%20corporations%20pay%20for%20the%20harms%20that%20they%20have%20caused%2C%26quot%3B%20Annika%20Martin%2C%20another%20lawyer%20for%20the%20plaintiffs%2C%20said.%20%26quot%3BBecause%20corporations%20are%20profit-seeking%20entities%2C%20hitting%20them%20in%20the%20wallet%20is%20the%20only%20way%20to%20influence%20their%20decision-making.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Felon-musk-grok-remove-clothes-ai-images-women-minors-backlash-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ExAI's%20Grok%20sparked%20massive%20backlash%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20the%20AI%20image%20generator%20was%20used%20to%20make%20nonconsensual%20sexualized%20images%20of%20real%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20response%2C%20X%2C%20the%20social%20media%20site%20that%20Musk%20sold%20to%20xAI%20in%20March%2C%20said%20Grok%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fgrok-stops-users-making-sexualized-ai-images-backlash-xai-musk-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eno%20longer%20be%20able%20to%20generate%20AI%20images%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20real%20people%20in%20sexualized%20or%20revealing%20clothing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftwitter-ad-revenue-scheme-creator-influencer-personalities-elon-musk-money-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EAshley%20St.%20Clair%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20gave%20birth%20to%20one%20of%20Elon%20Musk's%20sons%20in%202024%2C%20sued%20xAI%20in%20January%2C%20alleging%20that%20Grok%20generated%20sexually%20explicit%20deepfakes%20of%20her%20at%20users'%20request.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFrench%20authorities%20are%20also%20investigating%20Grok%20over%20sexualized%20deepfakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flawsuit-allegation-xai-grok-created-sexualized-deepfakes-minors-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773701670000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b85747a96e437d6eb86520%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flawsuit-allegation-xai-grok-created-sexualized-deepfakes-minors-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20proposed%20class%20action%20accuses%20Elon%20Musk%20and%20his%20AI%20star