0height%3D%5C%224480%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETK%3Cp%3Eeclipse_images%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWhen%20it%20came%20time%20to%20replace%20our%20bed%2C%20we%20decided%20not%20to%20splurge%20on%20a%20king-size%20mattress.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMy%20family%20spends%20a%20lot%20of%20quality%20time%20in%20bed%2C%20and%20I%20regret%20not%20upgrading%20when%20we%20had%20the%20chance.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20cherish%20these%20silly%20moments%20of%20connection%20and%20know%20they%20won't%20last%20forever.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Christmas%20one%20year%2C%20my%20husband%20and%20I%20bought%20our%20then%202-year-old%20son%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fparents-waiting-up-to-8-months-get-nugget-foam-couch-2020-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENugget%20Couch%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20was%20amazing%2C%20and%20more%20comfortable%20than%20our%20mattress.%20Wait%2C%20was%20our%20mattress%20really%20that%20bad%3F%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EI%20was%20pregnant%20and%20had%20thought%20it%20needed%20replacing%20(after%20all%2C%20it%20was%20over%2010%20years%20old)%2C%20but%20the%20play%20couch%20pushed%20us%20to%20make%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-mattress%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emattress%20purchase%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%2C%20on%20some%20days%2C%20I%20think%20we%20rushed%20into%20without%20considering%20some%20important%20things.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20chose%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-hybrid-mattresses%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Equeen%20mattress%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20same%20size%20as%20the%20one%20we%20were%20replacing.%20At%20the%20time%2C%20the%20king%20seemed%20like%20a%20luxury%20we%20didn't%20need.%20And%20we%20certainly%20didn't%20need%20to%20spend%20the%20extra%20money%2C%20either.%20Now%2C%20I%20see%20things%20differently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221ae8d3b7-8859-4811-8065-8365223d0ef5%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EAdding%20a%20second%20child%20changed%20the%20dynamics%20in%20our%20bed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20came%20time%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fhow-to-choose-a-mattress%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eshop%20for%20our%20new%20mattress%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20my%20husband%20casually%20mentioned%20upgrading%20our%20queen%20bed%20to%20a%20king%2C%20but%20I%20had%20little%20interest%2C%20and%20we%20never%20discussed%20it%20much%20past%20that.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EI've%20always%20felt%20like%20king-sized%20beds%20were%20too%20spacious.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Ftravel%2Fhotel-mattresses-you-can-buy-for-home%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAt%20hotels%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20they%20required%20scooting%20over%20to%20reach%20the%20center%20of%20the%20bed.%20Who%20wants%20to%20do%20that%3F%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EWe%20went%20with%20the%20queen%2C%20and%20things%20were%20fine%20for%20a%20while.%20After%20all%2C%20when%20just%20one%20child%20toddles%20into%20our%20room%20and%20climbs%20into%20bed%2C%20there%20are%20cuddles%20and%20coziness.%20However%2C%20when%20two%20children%20wind%20up%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffamily-co-sleeping-same-bed-experience-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ein%20our%20bed%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20there%20are%20feet%20in%20each%20other's%20faces%2C%20and%20everyone%20winds%20up%20a%20bit%20uncomfortable%2C%20especially%20now%20that%20they're%204%20and%206.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3ESometimes%20a%20child%20will%20wind%20up%20lying%20sideways.%20Once%2C%20I%20might%20have%20suggested%20that%20someone%20sleep%20at%20the%20end%20of%20the%20bed%2C%20where%20one%20might%20picture%20a%20dog%20or%20cat%20(neither%20of%20which%20we%20own).%20The%20extra%20space%20a%20king-sized%20mattress%20would%20provide%20sure%20would%20come%20in%20handy%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2248071e74-ecc2-4aa6-bb75-e263d3d3b4df%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20play%20games%20on%20our%20bed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20started%20a%20game%20with%20our%20kids%20where%20he%20pretends%20that%20our%20blanket%20is%20a%20%26quot%3Bhungry%20house%26quot%3B%20that%20will%20eat%20up%20and%20envelop%20them.%20The%20kids%20also%20love%20it%20when%20we%20pretend%20they're%20airplanes%20and%20toss%20them%20into%20the%20bed%2C%20where%20they%20squirm%20like%20rollie-pollies.%20These%20activities%20take%20up%20a%20lot%20of%20space%2C%20and%20having%20more%20room%20to%20roll%20around%20and%20play%20would%20be%20a%20plus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20in%20a%20blue%20moon%2C%20our%20kids%20will%20decide%20to%20bring%20all%20their%20stuffed%20animals%20into%20the%20bed%20and%20make%20a%20suffie%20mountain%2C%20or%20play%20hide-and-seek%20under%20the%20covers.%20Then%20there%20are%20the%20nights%20when%20our%20daughter%20climbs%20into%20our%20bed%20and%20announces%20herself%20with%20a%20doorbell%20sound.%20I%20cherish%20these%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchange-parenting-style-for-each-kid-different-approach-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esilly%20moments%20of%20connection%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20know%20they%20won't%20last%20forever%2C%20so%20I%20want%20to%20encourage%20them%20as%20much%20as%20possible%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221172%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20author%20poses%20while%20skiing.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b84c2da96e437d6eb863be%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22879%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20author%20says%20her%20family%20spends%20a%20lot%20of%20quality%20time%20in%20the%20bed%20she%20and%20her%20husband%20share.%20She%20now%20regrets%20not%20splurging%20on%20a%20king-sized%20mattress%20when%20she%20got%20a%20new%20bed.%3Cp%3ECourtesy%20of%20Anne%20James%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22da6e3977-ae83-4b02-9ce7-d151f905b45c%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EI%20feel%20like%20I%20missed%20our%20chance%20to%20upgrade%20to%20a%20king-size%20bed%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20four%20years%20later%2C%20I%20question%20why%20I%20didn't%20consider%20my%20husband's%20suggestion%20to%20upgrade%20to%20a%20king-size%20bed%20seriously.%20As%20an%20item%20that's%20only%20replaced%20every%2010%20years%20or%20so%2C%20and%20with%20a%20higher%20price%20tag%2C%20it's%20a%20big%20decision.%20%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EIt%20seems%20too%20late%20to%20change%20mattress%20sizes%20now%20since%20we'd%20need%20both%20a%20new%20bed%20frame%20and%20mattress%2C%20and%20it%20doesn't%20make%20sense%20to%20replace%20ours%2C%20which%20works%20perfectly%20fine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20some%20point%2C%20our%20kids%20will%20stop%20crawling%20into%20our%20bed.%20By%20the%20time%20we'll%20need%20a%20new%20mattress%20again%2C%20I%20likely%20won't%20feel%20the%20same%20desire%20or%20need%20for%20a%20king-size%20bed.%20But%20if%20I%20chose%20again%20with%20younger%20kids%2C%20I'd%20get%20a%20king.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-matress-size-for-families-king-vs-queen-young-kids-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773700441000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b8258aa7a4f9df67ba64ac%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-matress-size-for-families-king-vs-queen-young-kids-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22We%20got%20a%20new%20mattress%20and%20didn't%20splurge%20on%20a%20king.%20As%20parents%20of%20two%20kids%20who%20enjoy%20spending%20quality%20time%20in%20bed%20together%2C%20I%20regret%20that%20choice.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Anne%20James)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-matress-size-for-families-king-vs-queen-young-kids-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%