0Huang%20says%20companies%20can't%20ignore%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fclawdbot-ai-mac-mini-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EOpenClaw%20moment%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20company%20in%20the%20world%20today%20needs%20to%20have%20an%20OpenClaw%20strategy%2C%20an%20agentic%20system%20strategy%2C%26quot%3B%20Huang%20said%20during%20Nvidia's%202026%20GTC%20conference%20in%20San%20Jose%20on%20Monday.%20%26quot%3BThis%20is%20the%20new%20computer.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20offered%20deep%20praise%20for%20OpenClaw%2C%20previously%20known%20as%20Clawdbot%20and%20Moltbot%2C%20an%20open-source%20AI%20agent%20that%20has%20taken%20Silicon%20Valley%20by%20storm.%20Though%20OpenAI%20lured%20away%20OpenClaw%20creator%20Peter%20Steinberger%2C%20the%20service%20will%20live%20on%20as%20an%20open-source%20project.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOpenClaw%20has%20made%20it%20possible%20for%20us%20to%20create%20personal%20agents%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BThe%20implication%20is%20incredible.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20said%20that%20OpenClaw%20%26quot%3Bgave%20the%20industry%20exactly%20what%20it%20needed%20at%20exactly%20the%20time.%26quot%3B%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOpenClaw%20will%20do%20for%20AI%20what%20Windows%20did%20for%20personal%20computing%2C%20Huang%20said.%20He%20also%20compared%20OpenClaw%20to%20other%20influential%20technologies%2C%20such%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprofile-linus-torvalds-inventor-linux-software-operating-system%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELinux%20operating%20system%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-is-kubernetes-google-cloud-2019-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EKubernetes%20cloud%20project%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20HTML.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20made%20it%20possible%20for%20the%20entire%20industry%20to%20grab%20onto%20this%20open-source%20stack%20and%20go%20do%20something%20with%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Huang%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20said%20there's%20one%20big%20caveat%20about%20using%20OpenClaw%20that%20Nvidia%20has%20been%20working%20to%20address%3A%20security.%20Nvidia%20announced%20its%20spin%20on%20OpenClaw%2C%20called%20NemoClaw%2C%20which%20allows%20users%20to%20add%20privacy%20and%20security%20controls%20to%20their%20AI%20agents%2C%20or%20%26quot%3Bclaws.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20has%20a%20network%20guardrail%2C%20it%20has%20a%20privacy%20router%2C%20and%20as%20a%20result%2C%20we%20could%20protect%20and%20keep%20the%20claws%20from%20executing%20inside%20our%20company%2C%20and%20do%20it%20safely%2C%26quot%3B%20Huang%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20is%20promoting%20NemoClaw%20at%20its%20conference%20by%20hosting%20a%20%26quot%3Bbuild-a-claw%26quot%3B%20event%20where%20attendees%20can%20develop%20their%20own%20custom-made%20AI%20agent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOpenClaw%20brings%20people%20closer%20to%20AI%20and%20helps%20create%20a%20world%20where%20everyone%20has%20their%20own%20agents%2C%26quot%3B%20Steinberger%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20released%20by%20Nvidia.%20%26quot%3BWith%20Nvidia%20and%20the%20broader%20ecosystem%2C%20we're%20building%20the%20claws%20and%20guardrails%20that%20let%20anyone%20create%20powerful%2C%20secure%20AI%20assistants.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20made%20a%20host%20of%20other%20announcements%20at%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-gtc-ai-system-groq-technology-inference-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENvidia%20GTC%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Monday%2C%20including%20a%20new%20inference%20system%20that%20incorporates%20technology%20from%20Groq%2C%20an%20AI%20chip%20startup%20with%20which%20Nvidia%20made%20a%20%2420%20billion%20deal.%20He%20also%20projected%20%241%20trillion%20in%20demand%20for%20its%20Blackwell%20and%20Rubin%20AI%20chips%20through%202027.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bus