0change%20that%20would%20allow%20companies%20to%20be%20fast-tracked%20into%20the%20Nasdaq%20100%20index%20shortly%20after%20their%20initial%20public%20offering.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.reuters.com%2Fbusiness%2Ffinance%2Felon-musks-spacex-weighs-nasdaq-listing-after-seeking-early-index-entry-sources-2026-03-10%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%20follow-up%20report%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20week%20said%20that%20Elon%20Musk's%20SpaceX%20is%20leaning%20toward%20a%20Nasdaq%20listing%2C%20requesting%20quicker%20entry%20into%20the%20tech-heavy%20index.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fx.com%2Fmichaeljburry%2Fstatus%2F2032483200404992209%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBurry%20pointed%20to%20recent%20X%3C%2Fa%3E%20posts%20slamming%20the%20proposal%2C%20including%20one%20from%20Wall%20Street%20veteran%20George%20Noble%2C%20which%20he%20described%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bmust%20read.%26quot%3B%20Noble%20characterized%20the%20idea%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bshameless%26quot%3B%20manipulation%20of%20the%20index.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BCurrently%2C%20new%20public%20companies%20typically%20wait%20up%20to%20a%20year%20before%20they're%20eligible%20for%20major%20index%20inclusion%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2F%40georgenoble%2Fnote%2Fc-226667679%3Fr%3D4repfn%26utm_medium%3Dios%26utm_source%3Dnotes-share-action%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BThat%20waiting%20period%20exists%20for%20a%20reason.%20It%20lets%20the%20market%20establish%20real%20price%20discovery.%20It%20protects%20passive%20investors%20from%20being%20forced%20into%20untested%2C%20illiquid%20stocks.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENoble%20argued%20that%20the%20move%20to%20accelerate%20SpaceX's%20entry%20into%20the%20Nasdaq%20would%20be%20detrimental%20to%20investors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20S%26amp%3BP%20500%20requires%20companies%20to%20have%20at%20least%2050%25%20of%20shares%20available%20for%20public%20trading%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BIt%20requires%206%20to%2012%20months%20of%20seasoning.%20It%20uses%20free-float%20adjusted%20weighting%20so%20passive%20investors%20aren't%20buying%20phantom%20liquidity.%20Nasdaq%20is%20doing%20the%20exact%20opposite.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBurry%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsubstack.com%2Fhome%2Fpost%2Fp-190495016%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eshared%20another%3C%2Fa%3E%20post%20from%20anonymous%20Substack%20author%2C%20Keubiko%2C%20who%20argued%20that%20Nasdaq's%20proposal%20would%20benefit%20insiders%20at%20the%20expense%20of%20investors.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20index%20is%20applying%20a%20phantom%2C%20mega-dollar%20weighting%20to%20a%20restricted%2C%20tightly-held%20float.%20You%20are%20effectively%20forcing%20a%20firehose%20of%20mega-cap%20index%20capital%20through%20a%20garden%20hose%20of%20actual%20liquidity.%20It%20is%20a%20recipe%20for%20a%20massive%2C%20artificial%20supply-and-demand%20squeeze%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20passage%20flagged%20by%20Burry%20reads.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENasdaq's%20proposed%20rule%20would%20allow%20a%20company%20that%20has%20recently%20listed%20with%20the%20exchange%20to%20join%20the%20index%20if%20its%20market%20cap%20ranks%20among%20the%20top%2040%20current%20stocks%20currently%20listed.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fspacex-ipo-space-stocks-elon-musk-rklb-asts-fly-sats-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ESpaceX%20could%20IPO%20this%20year%3C%2Fa%3E%20with%20a%20valuation%20of%20more%20than%20%241.5%20trillion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20rules%20are%20being%20rewritten%20to%20benefit%20IPO%20issuers%20and%20early-stage%20insiders%2C%20and%20your%20capital%20is%20the%20tool%20being%20USED%20to%20enrich%20them%2C%20Noble%20said.%20%26quot%3B45%20years%20in%20this%20business%20and%20I've%20watched%20Wall%20Street%20find%20creative%20new%20ways%20to%20separate%20retail%20investors%20from%20their%20money%20in%20every%20cycle.%20But%20usually%20they%20at%20least%20try%20to%20be%20subtle%20about%20it.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20Nasdaq%20representative%20declined%20to%20comment.%20SpaceX%20did%20not%20reply%20to%20a%20request%20for%20comment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmichael-burry-nasdaq-spacex-ipo-listing-elon-musk-tesla-ndx-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773697329000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b817faa7a4f9df67ba632f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmichael-burry-nasdaq-spacex-ipo-listing-elon-musk-tesla-ndx-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Michael%20Burry%20said%20a%20post%20from%20veteran%20investor%20George%20Noble%20slamming%20a%20rule%20change%20floated%20by%20Nasdaq%20was%20a%20%26quot%3Bmust%20read.%26quot%3B%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sobrient%40insider.com%20(Samuel%20O'Brient)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmichael-burry-nasdaq-spacex-ipo-listing-elon-musk-tesla-ndx-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Horror%E2%80%99s%20Big%20Night%3A%20%E2%80%98Sinners%E2%80%99%20and%20%E2%80%98Weapons%E2%80%99%20Oscar%20Wins%20Have%20Filmmakers%20Celebrating%20the%20Genre%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773697202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236688961%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22When%20Amy%20Madigan%20accepted%20the%20first%20Oscar%20of%20the%20night%20during%20the%20March%2015%20ceremony%2C%20she%20shouted%20out%20her%20%E2%80%9CWeapons%E2%80%9D%20writer%20and%20director%20Zach%20Cregger%20for%20creating%20her%20witchy%20role%20of%20Aunt%20Gladys%2C%20saying%20he%20%E2%80%9Cwrote%20a%20dream%20part%2C%20and%20he%20let%20me%20just%20grab%20it%20by%20the%20throat.%E2%80%9D%20It%20seems%20that%2C%20after%20decades%20