0the%20first%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15118270397pvg-20%26h%3D8721594bf7c3bcbd57c3ef39b5420b181c0b3b0f98ca11f941b1256e425ce82f%26postID%3D69b851989e03109b8bec7ee1%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fdeals%252Fparamount-plus-deal-2026-3%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.paramountplus.com%252F%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EParamount%20Plus%20deal%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%20Black%20Friday%20and%20Cyber%20Monday%20in%202025%2C%20and%20it's%20the%20same%20deal%20that%20was%20offered%20on%20those%20major%20shopping%20holidays%2C%20so%20we%20don't%20expect%20to%20see%20a%20better%20sale%20on%20these%20monthly%20plans%20anytime%20soon.%20Given%20the%20January%202026%20Paramount%20Plus%20price%20hikes%2C%20wherein%20each%20monthly%20plan%20increased%20by%20%241%20a%20month%2C%20this%20is%20technically%20a%20better%20discount%20than%20the%20Black%20Friday%20deal.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20current%20offer%20will%20discount%20the%20first%20two%20months%20of%20service%20for%20new%20and%20former%20subscribers.%20After%20that%20period%20is%20up%2C%20plans%20will%20renew%20at%20the%20then-standard%20rate%2C%20which%20is%20currently%20%249%20a%20month%20for%20Essential%20and%20%2414%20a%20month%20for%20Premium.%20However%2C%20monthly%20subscribers%20can%20always%20cancel%20before%20then.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20not%20sure%20which%20plan%20to%20sign%20up%20for%2C%20we%20think%20it's%20worth%20giving%20a%20Premium%20subscription%20a%20go%20since%20it'll%20cost%20the%20same%20for%20two%20months.%20Streaming%20services%20rarely%20offer%20the%20same%20discount%20on%20both%20their%20ad-supported%20and%20ad-free%20tiers%20(and%20often%20forgo%20ad-free%20discounts%20altogether)%2C%20making%20this%20rare%20deal%20worth%20cashing%20in%20on.%20You%20can%20learn%20more%20about%20the%20streaming%20service%20and%20deal%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22ab6ef3bd-57a2-4d44-a53e-e209c254a6b7%5C%22%3EFAQ%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Ch3%3EWhen%20does%20the%20deal%20end%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Paramount%20Plus%20deal%20ends%20on%20March%2031%2C%202026%2C%20so%20potential%20customers%20have%20until%20the%20end%20of%20the%20month%20to%20cash%20in%20on%20the%20offer.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat's%20on%20Paramount%20Plus%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EParamount%20Plus%20is%20the%20streaming%20home%20of%20all%20things%20CBS%2C%20so%20new%20episodes%20of%20popular%20CBS%20shows%20(like%20%26quot%3BNCIS%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BMarshals%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BSurvivor%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BTracker%26quot%3B)%20will%20land%20on%20the%20service%20the%20day%20after%20their%20broadcasts.%20Fans%20can%20also%20watch%20these%20shows%20live%20with%20the%20Premium%20tier%2C%20which%20we'll%20dig%20into%20more%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20streaming%20service%20also%20hosts%20a%20slate%20of%20original%20content%2C%20most%20notably%20shows%20from%20Yellowstone%20creator%20Taylor%20Sheridan%2C%20including%20%26quot%3B1883%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3B1923%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BThe%20Madison%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BMayor%20of%20Kingstown%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BLandman%2C%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BLioness%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20%26quot%3BTulsa%20King.%26quot%3B%20Just%20keep%20in%20mind%20that%20you'll%20need%20to%20head%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstreaming%2Fpeacock-tv-streaming-service-app%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EPeacock%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20watch%20the%20original%20%26quot%3BYellowstone%26quot%3B%20series.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EParamount%20Plus%20also%20offers%20an%20impressive%20catalog%20of%20movies%2C%20along%20with%20select%20programming%20from%20other%20Paramount-owned%20networks%2C%20such%20as%20Comedy%20Central%20and%20MTV.%20With%20the%20Premium%20tier%2C%20you%20can%20also%20watch%20Showtime%20content.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditionally%2C%20the%20streamer%20offers%20an%20ever-growing%20selection%20of%20live%20sports%20content.%20Both%20tiers%20of%20service%20include%20access%20to%20NFL%20on%20CBS%20games%2C%20Champions%20League%20matches%2C%20and%20UFC%20events.%20If%20you%20want%20to%20watch%20every%20live%20sport%20that%20airs%20on%20CBS%2C%20you'll%20need%20to%20upgrade%20to%20a%20Premium%20plan.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch3%3EWhat's%20the%20difference%20between%20Paramount%20Plus%20Essential%20and%20Premium%3F%3C%2Fh3%3E%3Cp%3EParamount%20Plus%20Essential%20offers%20ad-supported%20access%20to%20all%20of%20the%20streaming%20service's%20on-demand%20content%2C%20except%20for%20most%20Showtime%20programming%2C%20which%20is%20available%20in%20the%20Premium%20tier.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20upgrading%20to%20Premium%2C%20you%20gain%20access%20to%20Showtime%20content%20and%20a%2024%2F7%20live%20stream%20of%20your%20local%20CBS%20station.%20Premium%20also%20unlocks%20ad-free%20on-demand%20streaming%20and%20the%20ability%20to%20download%20most%20content%20for%20offline%20viewing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3ETo%20learn%20more%2C%20you%20can%20explore%20our%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fstreaming%2Fparamount-plus-streaming-service-app%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EParamount%20Plus%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20guide%20or%20head%20directly%20to%20the%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Faffiliate.insider.com%2F%3FamazonTrackingID%3Dbi-auto-15118270397pvg-20%26h%3D8721594bf7c3bcbd57c3ef39b5420b181c0b3b0f98ca11f941b1256e425ce82f%26postID%3D69b851989e03109b8bec7ee1%26postSlug%3Dguides%252Fdeals%252Fparamount-plus-deal-2026-3%26tags%3Dservice%253Acapi%26u%3Dhttps%253A%252F%252Fwww.paramountplus.com%252F%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EParamount%20Plus%20website%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E.%20For%20additional%20sales%2C%20check%20out%20our%20roundup%20of%20the%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fdeals%2Fbest-streaming-deals-bundles%5C%22%20