0by%2035%20times%20and%20is%20shipping%20later%20this%20year%2C%20Huang%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang%20unveiled%20a%20new%20inference%20system%20at%20the%20company's%20annual%20GTC%20conference%20on%20Monday%20%E2%80%94%20the%20company's%20most%20decisive%20move%20yet%20to%20defend%20its%20dominance%20as%20inference%20becomes%20AI's%20next%20battleground.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20push%20into%20inference%20comes%20as%20Huang%20said%20Nvidia%20projects%20massive%20demand.%20The%20company%20expects%20at%20least%20%241%20trillion%20in%20demand%20for%20its%20Blackwell%20and%20Rubin%20AI%20systems%20through%202027%20%E2%80%94%20up%20from%20about%20%24500%20billion%20in%20projected%20demand%20through%202026%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20AI%20chip%20giant%20announced%20the%20new%20Nvidia%20Groq%203%20LPX%2C%20which%20Huang%20said%20can%20speed%20up%20inference%20workloads%20by%20up%20to%2035%20times.%20It%20integrates%20technology%20from%20AI%20chip%20startup%20Groq%20and%20pairs%20it%20with%20Nvidia's%20Vera%20Rubin%20architecture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESamsung%20manufactures%20the%20new%20Groq%20chip%2C%20and%20Nvidia%20expects%20the%20system%20to%20ship%20in%20the%20second%20half%20of%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20inflection%20point%20of%20inference%20has%20arrived%2C%26quot%3B%20Huang%20said%20at%20the%20keynote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia's%20new%20system%20builds%20on%20the%20roughly%20%2420%20billion%20deal%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-reaches-licensing-agreement-with-groq-hires-ai-top-talent-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estruck%20with%20Groq%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20December%2C%20which%20saw%20it%20license%20Groq's%20technology%20and%20hire%20its%20top%20engineers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHuang%20had%20previously%20hinted%20at%20a%20collaboration%20with%20startup%20Groq%20during%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiggest-takeaways-from-nvidias-q4-earnings-vera-rubin-chips-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ENvidia's%20latest%20earnings%20call%3C%2Fa%3E.%20The%20Wall%20Street%20Journal%20earlier%20reported%20that%20the%20company%20was%20preparing%20a%20new%20inference%20system%20incorporating%20Groq%20technology.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia's%20graphics%20processing%20units%20(GPUs)%20still%20dominate%20the%20AI%20field%20and%20can%20be%20used%20for%20both%20training%20AI%20models%20and%20inference%2C%20or%20how%20AI%20models%20make%20decisions%20or%20predictions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20a%20growing%20number%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-ai-dominance-rising-competition-from-rivals-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENvidia%20competitors%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20from%20hyperscalers%20to%20chip%20startups%20%E2%80%94%20are%20developing%20specialized%20systems%20that%20are%20cheaper%20and%20more%20efficient%20for%20the%20repetitive%20and%20cost-sensitive%20work%20of%20inference.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20rise%20of%20AI%20agents%20%E2%80%94%20or%20tools%20that%20conduct%20tasks%20on%20behalf%20of%20humans%20%E2%80%94%20could%20dramatically%20increase%20inference%20demand.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20this%20end%2C%20AI%20companies%20like%20OpenAI%20have%20explored%20alternatives%20to%20Nvidia%20hardware.%20Reuters%20previously%20reported%20that%20it%20was%20dissatisfied%20with%20the%20company's%20inference%20chips.%20In%20January%2C%20OpenAI%20signed%20a%20reported%20%2410%20billion%20compute%20deal%20with%20inference%20chip%20startup%20Cerebras.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Agweiss%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Egweiss%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20Signal%20at%20%40geoffweiss.25.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%2C%20a%20nonwork%20WiFi%20network%2C%20and%20a%20nonwork%20device%3B%20%3C%2F