%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsinners-box-office-ryan-coogler-deal-with-warner-bros-explained-2025-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebox-office%20hit%20%26quot%3BSinners.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20may%20seem%20counterintuitive%20that%20losing%20a%20prestigious%20award%20would%20be%20good%20for%20a%20celebrity's%20career%2C%20but%20in%20Chalamet's%20case%2C%20winning%20could've%20been%20much%20worse.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%2030%2C%20Chalamet%20has%20been%20nominated%20for%20best%20actor%20three%20times.%20During%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftimothee-chalamet-snl-oscar-awards-guerrilla-marketing-campaign-lime-bike-2025-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehis%20campaign%20for%20the%202024%20Bob%20Dylan%20biopic%20%26quot%3BA%20Complete%20Unknown%2C%26quot%3B%20Chalamet%3C%2Fa%3E%20said%20he%20was%20in%20%26quot%3Bpursuit%20of%20greatness%2C%26quot%3B%20naming%20Oscar%20winners%20Daniel%20Day-Lewis%2C%20Marlon%20Brando%2C%20and%20Viola%20Davis%20as%20his%20inspirations.%20He%20ultimately%20lost%20that%20bid%20to%20Adrien%20Brody%2C%20just%20as%20he%20lost%20his%20first%20acting%20nomination%20for%20his%20breakout%20role%20in%20%26quot%3BCall%20Me%20By%20Your%20Name%26quot%3B%20to%20Gary%20Oldman.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20time%20around%2C%20Chalamet%20doubled%20down%20on%20his%20guerrilla%20marketing%20tactics%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmarty-supreme-marketing-campaign-why-it-worked-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epromote%20%26quot%3BMarty%20Supreme%26quot%3B%20during%20awards%20season%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20attended%20red%20carpets%20dressed%20in%20bright%2C%20garish%20orange%20as%20a%20nod%20to%20his%20character's%20custom-colored%20ping-pong%20balls.%20He%20hosted%20an%20underground%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vanityfair.com%2Fhollywood%2Fstory%2Ftimothee-chalamet-lets-his-inner-sports-fan-fly-at-the-marty-supreme-invitational%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etable%20tennis%20tournament%3C%2Fa%3E.%20He%20was%20featured%20on%20a%20remix%20by%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpitchfork.com%2Fnews%2Fesdeekid-releases-remix-featuring-a-rapping-timothee-chalamet%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emysterious%20UK%20artist%20EsDeeKid%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20rapping%20about%20his%20success%20and%20Marty%20Mauser-sized%20ego%3A%20%26quot%3BMy%20life%20is%20an%20opera%2C%20look%20at%20the%20Oscars%20%2F%20Look%20at%20the%20groupies%2C%20look%20at%20the%20movies.%26quot%3B%20Finally%2C%20in%20late%20February%2C%20he%20enraged%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Ffilm%2F2026%2Fmar%2F09%2Ftimothee-chalamet-backlash-opera-and-ballet%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eopera%20singers%20and%20ballet%20dancers%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20he%20said%20%26quot%3Bno%20one%20cares%26quot%3B%20about%20those%20disciplines%20enough%20to%20properly%20fund%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20respect%20to%20the%20ballet%20and%20opera%20people%20out%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%20%26quot%3BI%20just%20lost%2014%20cents%20in%20viewership.%20I'm%20taking%20shots%20for%20no%20reason.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20of%20these%20stunts%20earned%20praise%20for%20Chalamet's%20hustle.%20Others%20drew%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.vulture.com%2Farticle%2Ftimothee-chalamet-wigga-marty-supreme-oscars.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeyerolls%20and%20backlash%3C%2Fa%3E.%20All%20attracted%20attention%2C%20of%20course%2C%20because%20that%20was%20the%20motivation%20all%20along.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Timoth%C3%A9e%20Chalamet%20applauds%20inside%20the%202026%20Oscars%20ceremony.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b841f9a7a4f9df67ba684a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETimoth%C3%A9e%20Chalamet%20applauds%20inside%20the%202026%20Oscars%20ceremony.%3Cp%3EKevin%20Winter%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2274083e2a-9d91-4441-86f5-a86cf2c8fafa%5C%22%3EChalamet%20was%20Oscar%20night's%20punching%20bag%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20spotlight%20had%20been%20trained%20on%20Chalamet%20for%20months%20leading%20up%20to%20the%20Oscars%2C%20and%20that%20scrutiny%20didn't%20stop%20when%20he%20arrived%20at%20the%20ceremony.%20Host%20Conan%20O'Brien%20didn't%20waste%20much%20time%20before%20cracking%20a%20joke%20at%20Chalamet's%20expense%3A%20%26quot%3BSecurity%20is%20extremely%20tight%20tonight.%20I'm%20told%20there%20are%20concerns%20about%20attacks%20from%20both%20the%20opera%20and%20ballet%20community%2C%26quot%3B%20O'Brien%20said%20in%20his%20opening%20monologue.%20He%20added%2C%20addressing%20Chalamet%20directly%2C%20%26quot%3BThey're%20just%20mad%20you%20left%20out%20jazz.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20director%20Alexandre%20Singh%20seemed%20to%20taunt%20Chalamet%20during%20his%20acceptance%20speech%20for%20best%20live-action%20short%20film%2C%20telling%20the%20crowd%2C%20%26quot%3BWe%20can%20change%20society%20through%20art%2C%20through%20creativity%2C%20through%20theater%20and%20ballet.%26quot%3B%20Legendary%20ballet%20dancer%20Misty%20Copeland%2C%20who'd%20previously%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F2026%2Ffilm%2Fglobal%2Fmisty-copeland-timothee-chalamet-actor-ballet-opera-1236684380%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erebuked%20Chalamet's%20comments%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20also%20took%20the%20stage%20to%20dance%20during%20a%20performance%20of%20the%20best%20original%20song%20nominee%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20Lied%20To%20You%2C%26quot%3B%20from%20%26quot%3BSinners.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChalamet%20took%20these%20slights%20on%20the%20chin%2C%20laughing%20genially%20at%20O'Brien's%20joke%20and%20giving%20both%20Copeland%20and%20Jordan%20a%20standing%20ovation.%20But%20taken%20together%2C%20Chalamet%20had%20a%20rough%20night.%20He%20was%20the%20ceremony's%20chosen%20punching%20bag.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChalamet%20has%20been%20in%20pursuit%20of%20an%20Oscar%20for%20nearly%20a%20decade%2C%20and%20he's%20been%20a%20serious%20contender%20more%20than%20once.%20If%20he'd%20finally%20won%20for%20%26quot%3BMarty%20Supreme%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20would've%20delivered%20that%20acceptance%20speech%20on%20his%20back%20foot.%20It's%20hard%20to%20imagine%20any%20serious%20actor%20wanting%20their%20long-awaited%20triumph%20on%20Hollywood's%20biggest%20stage%20to%20be%20eclipsed%20by%20a%20bout%20of%20negative%20press.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20if%20Chalamet%20had%20won%2C%20the%20negative%20press%20surely%20would%20have%20intensified.%20His%20win%20would%20be%20described%20as%20undeserving%20or%20ill-timed.%20The%20internet%20would%20be%20flooded%20with%20thinkpieces%20about%20his%20overexposure%20and%20his%20try-hard%20vibes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20the%20cruel%2C%20cyclical%20nature%20of%20celebrity%20culture%3A%20To%20succeed%20is%20to%20find%20a%20bigger%20target%20on%20your%20back.%20Audiences%20will%20inflate%20egos%20just%20for%20the%20pleasure%20of%20watching%20them%20pop.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EChalamet%20is%20already%20one%20of%20the%20most%20sought-after%20actors%20of%20his%20generation%2C%20and%20if%20he%20continues%20down%20this%20path%2C%20he'll%20be%20well%20positioned%20to%20finally%20win%20an%20Oscar%20someday.%20After%20all%2C%20the%20Academy's%20voters%20historically%20prefer%20to%20make%20men%20wait%20for%20their%20flowers%3B%20consider%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleonardo-dicaprio-oscar-win-2016-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ELeonardo%20DiCaprio%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20who%20was%20nominated%20in%20acting%20categories%20four%20times%20before%20he%20won%20at%2041%2C%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbradley-cooper-loses-best-actor-oscar-abbott-elementary-guest-star-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBradley%20Cooper%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%2051%2C%20who's%20still%20winless%20after%20five%20nominations.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Chalamet%20is%20aiming%20for%20a%20long%2C%20celebrated%20career%20in%20Hollywood%2C%20he%20can%20stand%20to%20wait%2C%20too%20%E2%80%94%20and%20perhaps%20even%20lay%20low%20for%20a%20while.%20Let%20the%20work%20speak%20for%20itself.%20Hopefully%2C%20if%20and%20when%20he%20takes%20home%20the%20gold%2C%20we'll%20be%20saying%20it%20was%20long%20overdue.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftimothee-chalamet-oscars-marty-supreme-best-actor-loss-analysis-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773693626000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b84215a96e437d6eb86256%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftimothee-chalamet-oscars-marty-supreme-best-actor-loss-analysis-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Timoth%C3%A9e%20Chalamet%20didn't%20win%20best%20actor%20at%20the%202026%20Oscars.%20Given%20his%20recent%20bout%20of%20negative%20press%2C%20his%20loss%20is%20actually%20a%20good%20thing.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22cahlgrim%40insider.com%20(Callie%20Ahlgrim)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftimothee-chalamet-oscars-marty-supreme-best-actor-loss-analysis-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Watch%3A%20Reunion%20resident%20gets%20close%20to%20lava%20from%20erupting%20volcano%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773693541000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F0a71%2Flive%2Fd9d3b7d0-2174-11f1-b297-95b0a0a8331e.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2Fc23zj1e0lxmo%233%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Lava%20from%20the%20Piton%20de%20la%20Fournaise%20volcano%20reached%20the%20Indian%20ocean%20for%20the%20first%20time%20in%2019%20years.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fn