3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EAfter%20totaling%20my%20car%2C%20my%20fianc%C3%A9%20and%20I%20decided%20we%20would%20share%20his%20in%20order%20to%20save%20money.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EI%20worried%20the%20arrangement%20would%20impact%20my%20freedom%20and%20independence%2C%20but%20it%20hasn't.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ESharing%20a%20car%20has%20improved%20our%20communication%20and%20helped%20us%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprofessional-wedding-planner-tips-saving-money-budget%5C%22%20data-autoaffiliated%3D%5C%22false%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esave%20money%20for%20a%20wedding%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20a%20home.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EOne%20week%20into%202026%2C%20I%20totaled%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbought-first-car-paid-cash-2024-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Efirst%20car%20I%20ever%20owned%3C%2Fa%3E%3A%20my%20beloved%2014-year-old%20Nissan%20Altima.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20logical%20next%20step%20would've%20been%20to%20start%20car%20shopping%2C%20but%20between%20planning%20a%20wedding%2C%20saving%20up%20for%20a%20house%2C%20and%20navigating%20a%20career%20shift%2C%202026%20was%20already%20shaping%20up%20to%20be%20expensive.%20Taking%20on%20a%20new%20car%20payment%20felt%20like%20working%20in%20direct%20opposition%20of%20my%20money-saving%20goals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20my%20fianc%C3%A9%20and%20I%20decided%20to%20share%20his%20car.%20Two%20months%20into%20our%20new%20arrangement%2C%20I%20can%20say%20it's%20been%20challenging%20but%20more%20worthwhile%20than%20I%20expected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227325a379-48fa-4645-b7b4-1a7bd2b88daa%5C%22%3EI%20worried%20that%20sharing%20a%20car%20would%20mean%20sacrificing%20independence%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Abby%20Lane%20partner%20(left)%20and%20Abby%20Lane%20at%20NFL%20game%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b812cb4d65ec51752a0e43%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EMy%20partner%20and%20I%20have%20been%20sharing%20a%20car%20for%20the%20past%20two%20months%2C%20and%20it%20requires%20significant%20planning.%3Cp%3EAbby%20Lane%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20live%20in%20an%20area%20that%20isn't%20particularly%20walkable%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftaking-public-transportation-solo-backpacking-europe-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Epublic%20transportation%3C%2Fa%3E%20isn't%20a%20reliable%20option.%20So%20before%20I%20got%20into%20the%20accident%2C%20my%20fianc%C3%A9%20and%20I%20were%20fortunate%20enough%20to%20operate%20as%20a%20two-car%20household.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHaving%20our%20own%20cars%20gave%20us%20freedom%2C%20spontaneity%2C%20and%20independence%20%E2%80%94%20three%20things%20I%20value%20in%20a%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20we%20decided%20to%20share%20a%20car%2C%20I%20worried%20I'd%20feel%20stuck%20at%20home%20if%20my%20partner%20had%20plans%20without%20me%20(and%20vice%20versa).%20What%20if%20we%20needed%20the%20car%20at%20the%20same%20time%3F%20Would%20having%20to%20coordinate%20every%20errand%20create%20tension%3F%20Would%20one%20of%20us%20quietly%20start%20to%20resent%20the%20other%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20immediate%20aftermath%20of%20the%20accident%2C%20I%20was%20still%20commuting%20an%20hour%20round-trip%20for%20work.%20My%20fianc%C3%A9%20works%20remotely%2C%20so%20the%20car%20defaulted%20to%20me%20most%20of%20the%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENow%2C%20we%20both%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwork-from-home-negotiate-flexible-remote-work-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ework%20from%20home%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20so%20things%20are%20less%20straightforward.%20No%20one%20has%20a%20claim%20over%20the%20car%20during%20business%20hours.%20Although%20that%20ambiguity%20can%20be%20frustrating%2C%20it's%20helped%20us%20be%20more%20mindful%20of%20each%20other's%20time%20and%20priorities%20and%20highlighted%20the%20ways%20we%20put%20one%20another%20first.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227f8abbca-37f3-471b-86a7-494f9311d068%5C%22%3EThe%20financial%20gains%20are%20worth%20the%20trade-offs%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20benefit%20of%20sharing%20a%20car%20is%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsuper-savers-early-retirement-best-money-saving-tips-financial-independence-2025-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emoney%20we're%20saving%3C%2Fa%3E.%20By%20not%20replacing%20my%20car%2C%20I%20avoided%20another%20monthly%20payment.%20Even%20leasing%20or%20financing%20a%20used%20vehicle%20could've%20easily%20led%20to%20me%20spending%20a%20few%20hundred%20dollars%20a%20month.%20I'm%20also%20sidestepping%20maintenance%2C%20registration%20fees%2C%20and%20inevitable%20repairs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20do%20occasionally%20spend%20money%20on%20rideshares%2C%20but%20those%20expenses%20are%20minimal%20compared%20to%20what%20it%20would%20cost%20to%20own%20and%20maintain%20a%20second%20car.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20month%20without%20an%20additional%20car%20payment%20is%20money%20we%20can%20put%20toward%20our%20wedding%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fmortgages%2Ftips-for-saving-for-a-down-payment%23%3A~%3Atext%3DYour%2520down%2520payment%2520plays%2520an%2Cand%2520your%2520monthly%2520payment%252C%2520too.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Edown%20payment%20funds%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It's%20given%20us%20a%20bit%20of%20breathing%20room.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20not%20to%20say%20it%20hasn't%20been%20challenging.%20Sharing%20one%20car%20means%20we%20have%20to%20coordinate%20almost%20everything%2C%20from%20grocery%20runs%20to%20social%20plans.%20It%20requires%20more%20check-ins%20than%20we're%20used%20to%2C%20but%20using%20a%20joint%20calendar%20and%20discussing%20plans%20further%20in%20advance%20has%20helped.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%221418b5a3-10c8-4c3a-b90b-a903a784a14b%5C%22%3ESharing%20a%20car%20has%20taught%20us%20to%20work%20together%20in%20new%20ways%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22828%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Abby%20Lane%20and%20her%20partner%20in%20their%20car%20-%20selfie%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b8137aa7a4f9df67ba6298%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221094%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETwo%20months%20into%20the%20arrangement%2C%20we're%20not%20in%20a%20rush%20to%20get%20another%20car.%3Cp%3EAbby%20Lane%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20last%20thing%20I%20expected%20was%20for%20my%20accident%20%E2%80%94%20and%20our%20subsequent%20decision%20to%20share%20a%20car%20%E2%80%94%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fways-methods-build-maintain-lasting-strong-bond-partner-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estrengthen%20my%20relationship%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20forced%20us%20to%20be%20intentional%20as%20we%20plan%20together%2C%20communicate%20openly%2C%20and%20navigate%20the%20occasional%20bump%20in%20the%20road.%20We're%20working%20as%20a%20team%20instead%20of%20living%20in%20our%20own%20little%20bubbles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20fianc%C3%A9%20has%20been%20incredibly%20generous%20and%20flexible%20throughout%20this%20transition.%20Watching%20him%20share%20without%20hesitation%2C%20and%20adjusting%20my%20own%20expectations%20in%20return%2C%20has%20made%20me%20pause%20and%20recognize%20how%20we%20show%20up%20for%20each%20other.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20don't%20expect%20we'll%20share%20a%20car%20forever%2C%20but%20I'm%20not%20in%20a%20rush%20to%20get%20my%20own.%20When%20I%20do%20start%20shopping%2C%20I%20want%20to%20choose%20one%20I'll%20keep%20for%20years%2C%20not%20just%20a%20quick%20replacement%20for%20the%20one%20I%20lost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20I%20don't%20anticipate%20making%20that%20purchase%20until%20after%20we've%20had%20our%20wedding%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbought-house-with-best-friend-good-idea-years-later-investment-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ebought%20a%20home%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20now%2C%20we're%20happy%20to%20trade%20a%20little%20comfort%20for%20space%20to%20save%2C%20plan%2C%20and%20focus%20on%20our%20shared%20goals.%20I've%20realized%20that%20true%20freedom%20and%20independence%20don't%20come%20from%20a%20single%20item%2C%20like%20a%20car%2C%20but%20from%20what%20we're%20building%20together%20in%20the%20long%20term.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsharing-car-with-partner-saving-money-challenges-benefits-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773690770000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b8126d4d65ec51752a0e33%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsharing-car-with-partner-saving-money-challenges-benefits-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22After%20my%20car%20was%20totaled%2C%20my%20fianc%C3%A9%20and%20I%20started%20sharing%20his%20car%20instead%20of%20buying%20a%20new%20one.%20The%20benefits%20have%20been%20worth%20the%20inconvenience.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Abby%20Lane)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsharing-car-with-partner-saving-money-challenges-benefits-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%E2%80%98Secret%20Lives%20of%20Mormon%20Wives%E2%80%99%20Pauses%20Season%205%20Filming%20Due%20to%20Domestic%20Violence%20Investigation%20Into%20Taylor%20Frankie%20Paul%20and%20Dakota%20Mortensen%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773690593000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2F%3Fp%3D1236690347%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Production%20has%20paused%20on%20Season%205%20of%20%E2%80%9CThe%20Secret%20Lives%20of%20Mormon%20Wives%E2%80%9D%20due%20to%20allegations%20of