tty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EVolvo%20is%20discontinuing%20the%20EX30%20and%20EX30%20Cross%20Country%20by%20year's%20end%2C%20the%20company%20said.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20car%20was%20first%20pitched%20as%20a%20%2435%2C000%20EV.%20Tariffs%20and%20trade%20wars%20complicated%20the%20price%20promise.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EAutomakers%20have%20reorganized%20their%20US%20EV%20lineups%20%E2%80%94%20and%20many%20have%20focused%20on%20their%20foreign-made%20cars.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Volvo%20EX30%20will%20exit%20stage%20left%20later%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Swedish%20automaker%20confirmed%20to%20Business%20Insider%20that%20it%20will%20end%20US%20sales%20of%20the%20EX30%20%E2%80%94%20its%20smallest%20and%20least%20expensive%20electric%20model%20%E2%80%94%20and%20the%20off-road-styled%20EX30%20Cross%20Country%20after%20the%202026%20model%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20said%20the%20vehicles%20will%20remain%20in%20production%20for%20the%20US%20through%20this%20summer%20and%20should%20stay%20on%20dealer%20lots%20through%20the%20end%20of%202026.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BVolvo%20Cars'%20commitment%20to%20electrification%20and%20our%20customers%20remains%20unchanged%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20company%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20sent%20to%20Business%20Insider.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20decision%20comes%20as%20several%20automakers%20reassess%20imported%20EVs%20following%20a%20turbulent%20stretch%20for%20the%20sector.%20A%20mix%20of%20tariffs%2C%20shifting%20incentives%2C%20and%20slowing%20demand%20has%20pushed%20companies%20to%20pause%20or%20cancel%20some%20electric%20models.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20EX30%20is%20the%20latest%20example.%20For%20years%2C%20its%20US%20rollout%20was%20complicated%20by%20shifting%20trade%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvolvo-ex30-electric-suv-tesla-rival-photos-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EVolvo%20unveiled%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20compact%20electric%20crossover%20in%202023%2C%20executives%20pitched%20it%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fevs-too-expensive-5-upcoming-affordable-models-kia-chevy-volvo-2024-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Erare%20affordable%20EV%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20American%20buyers%2C%20with%20a%20starting%20price%20below%20%2435%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20vehicle%20was%20initially%20earmarked%20for%20production%20in%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20in%202024%2C%20under%20the%20Biden%20administration%2C%20the%20US%20imposed%20a%20100%25%20tariff%20on%20electric%20vehicles%20imported%20from%20China%2C%20forcing%20Volvo%20to%20shift%20US-bound%20production%20to%20Belgium.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAdditional%20tariffs%20imposed%20during%20the%20Trump%20administration%20on%20all%20imported%20vehicles%20raised%20the%20cost%20of%20bringing%20the%20car%20back%20to%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20consumer%20price%20climbed%20as%20a%20result.%20Today%2C%20the%20EX30%20starts%20at%20about%20%2441%2C740%2C%20including%20destination.%20The%20Cross%20Country%20variant%20%E2%80%94%20which%20starts%20around%20%2450%2C000%20%E2%80%94%20only%20began%20arriving%20at%20US%20dealerships%20earlier%20this%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20model%20will%20continue%20selling%20in%20other%20markets%2C%20including%20Canada%20and%20Mexico.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20change%2C%20Volvo%20said%20its%20broader%20electrification%20strategy%20remains%20intact.%20The%20company%20has%20said%20it%20aims%20to%20have%2090%25%20to%20100%25%20of%20its%20global%20sales%20come%20from%20vehicles%20with%20an%20electrical%20socket%20%E2%80%94%20a%20mix%20of%20plug-in%20hybrids%20and%20fully%20electric%20cars%20%E2%80%94%20by%202030.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20automaker%20is%20also%20preparing%20to%20add%20new%20options%20to%20its%20US%20EV%20lineup.%20Volvo%20expects%20its%20new%20electric%20SUV%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvolvo-ex60-ev-electric-suv-specs-range-photos-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ethe%20EX60%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20to%20arrive%20this%20summer%20with%20up%20to%20400%20miles%20of%20range%20and%20a%20starting%20price%20of%20around%20%2455%2C000.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%2202c454f8-f1ab-4a36-baa8-3934b52c371d%5C%22%3EEVs%20under%20the%20microscope%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228164%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20silver%20Hyundai%20Kona%20electric%20is%20parked%20inside%20a%20dealership%20showroom%20next%20to%20a%20Hyundai%20Ioniq%205%20SUV.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b842d3a7a4f9df67ba6866%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%226123%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAutomakers%20have%20been%20rejigging%20their%20EV%20lineups%20at%20US%20dealerships.%20Foreign-made%20EVs%20have%20been%20some%20of%20the%20first%20cars%20to%20get%20the%20ax.%3Cp%3ENICOLAS%20GUYONNET%2FHans%20Lucas%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EVolvo's%20decision%20arrives%20during%20a%20difficult%20stretch%20for%20EV%20sales%20in%20the%20US.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20CarGurus%20data%2C%20dealership%20EV%20sales%20were%20down%2053.5%25%20and%2045.2%25%20in%20the%20first%20two%20months%20of%20the%20year%20compared%20with%20the%20same%20time%20period%20in%202025.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESales%20have%20been%20in%20a%20slump%20since%20September%2C%20when%20the%20federal%20government%20canceled%20the%20%247%2C500%20tax%20credit%20for%20electric%20vehicles.%20Automakers%20have%20responded%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fevs-automakers-axed-this-year-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eremoving%20cars%20from%20their%20US%20lineup%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20especially%20foreign-built%20vehicles.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EVolkswagen%20has%20temporarily%20stopped%20sending%20the%20German-built%20ID.%20Buzz%20minivan%20to%20the%20US.%20Nissan%20axed%20the%20Japan-built%20Ariya.%20Hyundai%20also%20stopped%20sending%20the%20Korean-built%20standard%20Ioniq%206%20to%20US%20lots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeth%20Goldstein%2C%20an%20EV%20industry%20analyst%20at%20Morningstar%2C%20said%20he%20expects%20more%20automakers%20to%20pull%20electric%20vehicles%20from%20the%20US%20market%20this%20year.%20But%20he%20also%20said%20lower-priced%20models%20could%20help%20revive%20the%20market%20in%20the%20coming%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20decision%20to%20discontinue%20the%20EX30%20was%20part%20of%20a%20shifting%20EV%20landscape%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BI%20expect%20we%20see%20US%20EV%20sales%20fall%20in%202026%2C%20but%20rise%20in%202027.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20rising%20gas%20prices%20could%20nudge%20some%20drivers%20back%20toward%20electric%20vehicles.%20As%20tensions%20in%20the%20Strait%20of%20Hormuz%20push%20up%20fuel%20costs%2C%20early%20indicators%20suggest%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhigher-gas-prices-lift-interest-in-electric-cars-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eshoppers%20may%20reconsider%20EVs%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEarly%20signs%20suggest%20that%20rising%20gas%20prices%20may%20be%20prompting%20some%20shoppers%20to%20reconsider%20EVs%2C%26quot%3B%20Kevin%20Roberts%2C%20CarGurus'%20director%20of%20economic%20and%20market%20intelligence%2C%20previously%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BOver%20the%20past%20several%20days%2C%20we've%20seen%20a%20lift%20in%20shopper%20views%20of%20EV%20listings.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvolvo-cancels-ex30-ev-electric-cars-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773689657000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b82d58a7a4f9df67ba65bd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fvolvo-cancels-ex30-ev-electric-cars-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Volvo%20con