20hi%20to%20some%20regulars.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20husband%20leaned%20over%20and%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BI%20love%20this.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20year%20before%2C%20we%20had%20been%20wall-to-wall%20at%20a%20roller-rink%20club%20in%20Brooklyn.%20Although%20we%20had%20a%20good%20time%2C%20sitting%20in%20that%20small-town%20restaurant%20%E2%80%94%20watching%20fireworks%20over%20the%20river%20%E2%80%94%20felt%20like%20exactly%20where%20we%20were%20meant%20to%20be.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20no%20line%2C%20cover%20fee%2C%20or%20wild%20countdown.%20The%20night%20that%20often%20disappoints%20simply%20didn't.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20wasn't%20where%20we%20thought%20we'd%20be%20on%20the%20last%20night%20of%202025.%20In%20June%2C%20we'd%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-to-sweden-lifestyle-work-culture-changes-2025-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emoved%20from%20New%20York%20to%20Sweden%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20just%20four%20months%20later%2C%20we%20found%20ourselves%20leaving%20for%20Maine.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%228a5f7b3f-5c7a-43f9-9c39-3f0be7d44da6%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EWe%20thought%20Sweden%20would%20be%20our%20new%20home%2C%20but%20circumstances%20made%20it%20temporary%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoved-to-sweden-from-the-us-culture-shock-2023-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMoving%20to%20Sweden%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20June%2C%20I%20was%20following%20a%20simple%20idea%3A%20When%20things%20feel%20scary%20in%20America%2C%20the%20best%20course%20of%20action%20is%20to%20leave.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20a%20while%2C%20it%20worked.%20Life%20felt%20gentler.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20fell%20into%20a%20mellow%20rhythm%2C%20going%20to%20the%20beach%2C%20visiting%20the%20many%20well-maintained%20conservation%20areas%20%E2%80%94%20including%20some%20that%20go%20directly%20through%20cow%20pastures%20%E2%80%94%20and%20eating%20affordable%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Freference%2Fhow-to-eat-healthy-on-a-budget%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ehealthy%20food%3C%2Fa%3E%20from%20the%20grocery%20store.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAlthough%20Sweden%20delivered%20in%20real%20ways%2C%20staying%20required%20logistical%20planning%20and%20more%20time%20than%20we%20had.%20Leaving%20didn't%20feel%20like%20failure%2C%20but%20choosing%20something%20more%20permanent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBack%20in%20the%20US%2C%20we%20weren't%20looking%20for%20another%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fleast-favorite-us-cities-according-to-frequent-traveler%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emajor%20metropolitan%20area%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20but%20a%20real%20community.%20That%20search%20led%20us%20to%20a%20small%20Maine%20city%20just%20south%20of%20Portland%2C%20where%20some%20of%20our%20friends%20were%20already%20living.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20population%20of%20under%2023%2C000%2C%20it%20sounded%20like%20a%20great%20fit.%20Friends%20helped%20us%20secure%20an%20apartment%20before%20we%20even%20arrived.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%224d46efb3-e157-451c-87c5-b34d8464cbb3%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20community%20here%20immediately%20felt%20unlike%20anywhere%20else%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%228660%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20street%20with%20storefronts%20in%20Biddeford%2C%20Maine.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b2d6474d65ec517529e531%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%225773%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3Ecaptiontk%3Cp%3EDenisTangneyJr%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20had%20a%20rich%20community%20in%20New%20York%2C%20but%20our%20friends%20were%20more%20spread%20out%20around%20the%20city.%20As%20soon%20as%20we%20got%20to%20Maine%2C%20though%2C%20we%20realized%20we%20could%20walk%20almost%20anywhere%3A%20from%20our%20apartment%20to%20a%20friend's%20place%2C%20the%20pharmacy%2C%20a%20grocery%20store%2C%20and%20the%20river.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20a%20result%2C%20our%20city%20really%20feels%20like%20home.%20Now%2C%20our%20friends'%20bakery%20isn't%20just%20a%20place%20to%20get%20delicious%20treats%20and%20coffee%3B%20it's%20where%20we%20run%20into%20%E2%80%94%20or%20make%20%E2%80%94%20friends%20in%20line%2C%20and%20chat%20about%20how%20their%20winter%20is%20going.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe've%20also%20seen%20the%20way%20Mainers%20support%20each%20other%20firsthand.%20When%20our%20moms%20came%20to%20visit%2C%20we%20took%20them%20for%20a%20coastal%20drive%20in%20our%20brand-new%20Volvo%20and%20slid%20straight%20into%20a%20ditch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20were%20inches%20from%20doing%20damage%20and%20bracing%20for%20a%20tow%20when%20a%20woman%20and%20her%20kids%20came%20outside%20and%20jumped%20in%20to%20help%20push%20us%20back%20onto%20the%20road.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWithin%20minutes%2C%20we%20were%20free.%20They%20waved%20while%20we%20drove%20off%20as%20if%20it%20were%20the%20most%20normal%20thing%20in%20the%20world.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOur%20community%20shows%20up%20for%20people%20in%20larger-scale%20ways%2C%20too.%20When%20a%20major%20fire%20hit%20the%20Old%20Port%20this%20winter%2C%20destroying%20boats%20and%20fishing%20equipment%2C%20the%20owner%20of%20a%20local%20seafood%20restaurant%20started%20selling%20T-shirts%2C%20with%20proceeds%20going%20to%20the%20fishermen%20affected.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMore%20recently%2C%20amid%20Immigration%20and%20Customs%20Enforcement%20(ICE)'s%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fice-has-ended-increased-enforcement-in-maine-susan-collins-2026-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eenhanced%20presence%20in%20Maine%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20residents%20responded%20immediately.%20Businesses%20put%20up%20%26quot%3BNo%20ICE%26quot%3B%20posters%2C%20a%20hotline%20was%20established%20to%20provide%20help%20and%20resources%2C%20and%20crowds%20gathered%20downtown%20to%20protest%20the%20occupation.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20reaffirmed%20what%20I%20already%20knew%20about%20Maine%3A%20When%20people%20here%