20in%20freedom%20with%20limits%20and%20has%20increased%20its%20moderation%20%26quot%3Btenfold.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20livestreamer%20Clavicular%20%E2%80%94%20who%20was%20once%20filmed%20running%20into%20someone%20with%20his%20Cybertruck%20%E2%80%94%20is%20the%20kind%20of%20provocative%20creator%20most%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fconservative-crackdown-forces-ad-industry-brand-safety-reset-2025-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emajor%20brands%3C%2Fa%3E%20won't%20touch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20hasn't%20stopped%20him%20from%20making%20serious%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%2020-year-old%20says%20he's%20pulled%20in%20more%20than%20%24100%2C000%20a%20month%20on%20Kick%2C%20his%20primary%20streaming%20platform%2C%20where%20he's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Flooksmaxxing-tiktok-trend-explained-men-trade-beauty-tips-2023-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eknown%20for%20%26quot%3Blooksmaxxing%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20or%20going%20to%20extreme%20measures%20to%20maximize%20attractiveness.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EClavicular%2C%20whose%20real%20name%20is%20Braden%20Peters%2C%20isn't%20alone.%20Kick%20has%20become%20a%20haven%20for%20some%20creators%20who%20are%20fed%20up%20with%20%E2%80%94%20or%20have%20been%20banned%20from%20%E2%80%94%20other%20platforms%2C%20particularly%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftwitch-ceo-dan-clancy-profitability-livestreaming-future-under-amazon-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAmazon-owned%20Twitch%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKick's%20payouts%20are%20a%20crucial%20revenue%20source%20for%20these%20creators%2C%20unlike%20the%20brand%20deals%20that%20serve%20as%20the%20backbone%20of%20the%20broader%20creator%20economy.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finfluencermarketinghub.com%2Fcreator-earnings-report-2025%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EA%202025%20survey%3C%2Fa%3E%20found%20that%20brands%20fund%20nearly%20three-quarters%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fcreator-platforms-make-more-money-old-media-wpp-2025-6%23%3A~%3Atext%3DThe%2520forecast%2520also%2520estimates%2520that%2520the%2520ad%2Cbillion%2520in%25202025%252C%2520up%252020%2525%2520from%25202024.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecreators'%20revenue%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20making%20Kick%20a%20lifeline%20for%20those%20considered%20%26quot%3Bunsafe%26quot%3B%20by%20mainstream%20brands.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAustralia-based%20Kick%2C%20founded%20in%202022%20by%20the%20owners%20of%20the%20crypto%20gambling%20site%20Stake.com%2C%20features%20lighter%20content%20moderation%20than%20some%20rivals%20and%20a%20generous%20pay%20structure%3A%20a%2095%2F5%20subscription%20revenue%20split%2C%20compared%20to%20rival%20Twitch's%20default%2050%2F50%20split.%20Kick%20says%20it%20may%20permit%20some%20violence%20depending%20on%20the%20context%2C%20for%20example%2C%20while%20Twitch%20says%20it%20has%20a%20%26quot%3Bzero-tolerance%26quot%3B%20policy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKick%20also%20makes%20direct%20payments%20to%20creators%20based%20on%20their%20viewership.%20The%20platform%20said%20it%20made%20%24182%20million%20in%20these%20payments%20between%20August%202023%20and%20the%20end%20of%20February.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20audience%20is%20growing%20fast%2C%20too%3A%20Kick%20nearly%20doubled%20its%20share%20of%20hours%20watched%20to%2012.4%25%2C%20or%204.5%20billion%20hours%20in%202025%2C%20according%20to%20a%20Stream%20Hatchet%20report.%20That%20made%20it%20the%20third-largest%20live-streaming%20platform%20by%20share%20of%20hours%20watched%2C%20behind%20Twitch%20at%2052%25%20and%20YouTube%20Gaming%20at%2024%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKick%20says%20it%20believes%20in%20freedom%20within%20limits.%20The%20platform%2C%20which%20is%20trying%20to%20smooth%20the%20way%20for%20ad%20deals%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20it's%20increased%20its%20human%20moderation%20team%20%26quot%3Btenfold%26quot%3B%20since%202022%20and%20that%20it%20responds%20quickly%20to%20creators%20in%20its%20live%20support%20chat.%20(Kick%20briefly%20suspended%20Clavicular%20in%20December%202025%2C%20after%20the%20video%20in%20which%20he%20ran%20into%20someone.%20Police%20investigated%20the%20scene%20and%20didn't%20file%20charges.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Adin%20Ross%20and%20N3on%2C%20center%2C%20known%20for%20their%20inflammatory%20comments%2C%20found%20popularity%20on%20Kick.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b83654a7a4f9df67ba66fa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAdin%20Ross%20and%20N3on%2C%20center%2C%20known%20for%20their%20inflammatory%20comments%2C%20found%20popularity%20on%20Kick.%3Cp%3EAllen%20Berezovsky%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EKick%20has%20also%20begun%20signing%20more%20brand-safe%20gamers%20and%20organizing%20events%20for%20creators%2C%20sponsoring%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-formula-one-became-powerhouse-in-entertainment-culture-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EFormula%201%20team%3C%2Fa%3E%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKick%20has%20started%20to%20legitimize%20itself%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mustafa%20Aijaz%2C%20VP%20at%20online%20gaming%20organization%20SoaR%20Gaming%2C%20which%20has%20multiple%20players%20using%20the%20platform%20alongside%20Twitch.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227d79e2b0-9dea-4925-9380-562ddc9ddeba%5C%22%3EThe%20manosphere%20is%20thriving%20on%20Kick%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EClavicular%20wasn't%20always%20on%20Kick.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20started%20his%20rise%20to%20online%20fame%20by%20posting%20on%20Looksmax.org%2C%20a%20forum%20where%20people%20rate%20each%20other%20and%20ask%20for%20advice%20on%20improving%20their%20appearance%20before%20going%20out.%20He%20now%20runs%20a%20paid%20online%20academy%20that%20provides%20looksmaxxing%20advice%20and%20guides%20to%20picking%20up%20women%2C%20which%20he