20casual%20games%20like%20Pok%C3%A9mon%20next%20to%20a%20video%20of%20someone%20playing%20slots.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou'll%20also%20likely%20come%20across%20videos%20from%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ftrump-son-barron-told-him-talk-to-streamer-adin-ross-2024-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAdin%20Ross%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%2025%2C%20who%20ranks%20as%20Kick's%20second-most%20popular%20streamer%2C%20according%20to%20Stream%20Charts.%20He%20has%20said%20his%20deal%20with%20Kick%20pays%20him%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fshorts%2F81QZNpegMoc%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efive%20figures%3C%2Fa%3E%20per%20hour%20he%20streams.%20He%20rose%20to%20fame%20by%20streaming%20NBA%202K%20and%20GTA%20V%20before%20moving%20into%20long%2C%20unfiltered%20interviews%20with%20celebrities%20like%20LeBron%20James%20and%20Logan%20Paul.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202024%2C%20he%20gave%20then-candidate%20Donald%20Trump%20a%20Cybertruck%20and%20tried%20to%20grow%20his%20support%20among%20young%20men.%20Ross%20buddied%20up%20with%20Tate%20and%20has%20streamed%20with%20Fuentes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERoss%20was%20banned%20by%20Twitch%20in%202023%20for%20not%20deleting%20multiple%20racist%20and%20antisemitic%20comments%20in%20his%20chat.%20Ross%20has%20said%20he%20takes%20accountability%20for%20the%20behavior%20of%20his%20fans.%20He%20also%20apologized%20after%20a%20clip%20of%20him%20making%20what%20appeared%20to%20be%20a%20Nazi%20salute%20circulated%20on%20X.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224284%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22LEEDS%2C%20ENGLAND%20-%20JANUARY%2020%3A%20Harrison%20(HStikkytokky)%20Sullivan%20looks%20on%20during%20the%20MF%20%26amp%3B%20DAZN%20X%20Series%20at%20First%20Direct%20Arena%20on%20January%2020%2C%202024%20in%20Leeds%2C%20England.%20(Photo%20by%20George%20Wood%2FGetty%20Images)%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b835144d65ec51752a1295%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222856%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EHarrison%20(HStikkytokky)%20Sullivan%20has%20built%20a%20image%20around%20insulting%20women.%3Cp%3EGeorge%20Wood%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAnother%20prominent%20Kick%20streamer%20is%20Harrison%20Sullivan%2C%20or%20HSTikkytokky%2C%20a%2024-year-old%20British%20influencer%20who%20started%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20health%20and%20fitness%20and%20has%20since%20built%20his%20brand%20around%20flirting%20with%20and%20insulting%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESullivan%2C%20who%20has%20been%20suspended%20from%20Kick%20multiple%20times%2C%20including%20for%20using%20homophobic%20slurs%20and%20showing%20sexually%20explicit%20content%2C%20now%20has%20242%2C000%20followers%20on%20the%20platform%2C%20where%20he%20often%20streams%20about%20gambling%20and%20women.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20views%20are%20sometimes%20hard%20to%20follow.%20For%20example%2C%20in%20one%20video%2C%20he%20denied%20being%20homophobic%20and%20racist%20in%20response%20to%20an%20earlier%20video%20where%20he%20maintained%20he%20was%20homophobic%20as%20well%20as%20antisemitic.%20He%20recently%20gained%20wider%20exposure%20as%20a%20subject%20of%20the%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnetflix-streamers-pull-back-done-with-political-documentaries-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ENetflix%20doc%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%26quot%3BLouis%20Theroux%3A%20Inside%20the%20Manosphere.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20there's%20N3on%2C%2021%2C%20whose%20real%20name%20is%20Rangesh%20Mutama.%20He%20started%20streaming%20as%20a%20teen%20gamer%20and%20has%20since%20shifted%20to%20real-life%20streaming%20marked%20by%20outlandish%20and%20inflammatory%20stunts%20%E2%80%94%20like%20faking%20his%20own%20death.%20He%20has%20nearly%20500%2C000%20followers%20on%20Kick%2C%20where%20he's%20also%20faced%20at%20least%20one%20suspension.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe's%20gotten%20some%20mainstream%20attention%20by%20hanging%20out%20with%20the%20ex-rapper%20Iggy%20Azalea%2C%20creating%20content%20with%20other%20rappers%2C%20and%20going%20on%20%26quot%3BThe%20Breakfast%20Club%2C%26quot%3B%20where%20he%20was%20called%20out%20for%20people%20leaving%20racist%20comments%20in%20his%20chat.%20N3on%20responded%20that%20the%20chat%20wasn't%20representative%20of%20his%20community%2C%20and%20he%20said%20he%20was%20evolving%20from%20a%20person%20who%20used%20to%20say%20whatever%20he%20wanted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EKick%20isn't%20alone%20in%20platforming%20controversial%20streamers%20who%20have%20been%20barred%20from%20other%20sites.%20Ross%20also%20streams%20on%20YouTube.%20Kicked%20off%20mainstream%20platforms%2C%20Fuentes%20streams%20to%20nearly%20700%2C000%20followers%20on%20Rumble.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221848%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Steven%20Bonnell%2C%20who%20goes%20by%20Destiny%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b83852a96e437d6eb8612c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221578%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESteven%20Bonnell%2C%20who%20goes%20by%20Destiny%2C%20built%20a%20following%20for%20his%20debate-heavy%20streams.%3Cp%3EJubilee%20via%20YouTube%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22c341b5c6-1653-4920-8d73-b30b95e7e58b%5C%22%3E%3Cstrong%3EStreamers%20span%20the%20political%20spectrum%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EKick%20is%20home%20to%20provocative%20streamers%20of%20many%20political%20and%20ideological%20persuasions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESteven%20Bonnell%2C%20aka%20Destiny%2C%20is%20a%20political%20creator%20who%20built%20a%20following%20with%20his%20debate-focused%20streams.%20The%2037-year-old%20advocates%20for%20some%20liberal%20policies%2C%20but%20isn't%20easily%20pigeonholed%20politically.%20He%20said%20he%20was%20suspended%20from%20Twitch%20in%202018%20after%20using%20homophobic%20and%20racist%20language%2C%20then%20permanently%20banned%20in%202022.%20He's%20also%20streamed%20a%20generally%20friendly%20discussion%20with%20Fuentes.%20Today%2C%20Destiny%20streams%20to%20133%2C000%20followers%20on%20Kick.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwho-is-xqc-twitch-most-popular-notorious-streamer-2021-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eprominent%20streamer%20xQc%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20whose%20real%20name%20is%20F%C3%A9lix%20Lengyel.%20XQc%2C%2030%2C%20gained%20online%20celebrity%20as%20a%20pro%20Overwatch%20player%20before%20getting%20an%20up%20to%20%24100%20million%20payday%20from%20Kick%20in%20one%20of%20the%20platform's%20biggest%20deals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20not%20overtly%20political%2C%20he's%20called%20people%20who%20voted%20for%20Trump%20a%20slur%20for%20the%20developmentally%20disabled.%20Early%20in%20his%20career%2C%20he%20made%20a%20widely%20criticized%20homophobic%20remark%2C%20for%20which%20he%20apologized.%20Years%20later%2C%20he%20expressed%20disapproval%20of%20homophobic%20remarks%20by%20fans%20in%20another%20online%20personality's%20stream.%20Morrison%2C%20xQc's%20manager%2C%20said%20he%20is%20%26quot%3Bloud%20and%20crazy%26quot%3B%20but%20added%20that%20he%20has%20%26quot%3Bnot%20a%20sliver%26quot%3B%20in%20common%20with%20the%20alt-right.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222656%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22SAN%20DIEGO%2C%20CALIFORNIA%20-%20SEPTEMBER%2021%3A%20Felix%20Lengyel%2C%20aka%20XQC%2C%20attends%20TwitchCon%202024%20San%20Diego%20on%20September%2021%2C%202024%20in%20San%20Diego%2C%20California.%20(Photo%20by%20Robin%20L%20Marshall%2FGetty%20Images)%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b838c84d65ec51752a1313%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221992%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EF%C3%A9lix%20Lengyel%2C%20aka%20xQc%2C%20is%20one%20of%20Kick's%20highest-paid%20streamers.%3Cp%3ERobin%20L%20Marshall%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhatever%20the%20politics%20or%20nature%20of%20their%20controversies%2C%20a%20common%20thread%20among%20many%20top%20Kick%20streamers%20is%20behavior%20that%20pushes%20the%20boundaries%20of%20social%20acceptance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BKick%20is%20like%20the%20Wild%20West%20of%20streaming%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Eric%20Harper%2C%20CEO%20of%20esports%20firm%20GG%20Talent%20Group.%20%26quot%3BSome%20of%20the%20biggest%20names%20on%20the%20platform%20have%20been%20ostracized%20from%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20gaming%20community%20because%20of%20hateful%20views%2C%20hateful%20actions.%20The%20TLDR%20is%2C%20there's%20a%20huge%20brand%20risk%2C%20which%20is%20why%20a%20lot%20of%20streamers%20don't%20stream%20there.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoney-moderation-streamers-clavicular-flock-to-kick-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773682179000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b82a77a7a4f9df67ba6552%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoney-moderation-streamers-clavicular-flock-to-kick-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Kick%20has%20become%20a%20haven%20for%20some%20creators%20who%20are%20fed%20up%20with%2C%20or%20have%20been%20banned%20from%2C%20other%20platforms%2C%20particularly%20Amazon's%20Twitch.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22lmoses%40insider.com%20(Lucia%20Moses)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoney-moderation-streamers-clavicular-flock-to-kick-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Mexico%20City%20breaks%20Guinness%20Record%20with%20giant%20football%20training%20session%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773681807000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fichef.bbci.co.uk%2Fnews%2F1024%2Fbranded_news%2F830b%2Flive%2Fc9dd7e00-215c-11f1-a79a-77e93010d956.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.bbc.com%2Fnews%2Fvideos%2Fcy7jrymgpjyo%233%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Mexico%20City%20set%20a%20Guinness%20record%20for%20the%2