kerberg%20has%20gone%20all%20in%20on%20AI.%3Cp%3EChris%20Unger%2FZuffa%20LLC%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EMeta%20might%20not%20yet%20have%20the%20best%20AI%20models%2C%20but%20it%20could%20be%20winning%20on%20another%20crucial%20front.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EMeta%20is%20considering%20major%20layoffs%20across%20the%20company%2C%20Business%20Insider%20reported.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EA%20top%20analyst%20suggested%20these%20cuts%20could%20signal%20that%20Meta's%20AI%20transformation%20is%20underway.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ECould%20more%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-weighing-major-layoffs-as-it-pours-billions-into-ai-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EMeta%20layoffs%3C%2Fa%3E%20mean%20the%20company%20still%20has%20bloat%20to%20trim%20%E2%80%94%20or%20could%20it%20signal%20its%20AI%20investments%20are%20actually%20starting%20to%20pay%20off%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20note%20from%20a%20top%20Wall%20Street%20analyst%20said%20on%20Monday%20that%20any%20head%20count%20cutting%20from%20Meta%20could%20actually%20be%20a%20sign%20that%20it's%20successfully%20rebuilding%20itself%20as%20an%20%26quot%3BAI-forward%26quot%3B%20company.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20could%20be%20bad%20for%20its%20rivals.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20Meta's%20deep%20investment%20in%20AI%20has%20so%20far%20not%20produced%20leading%20models%20like%20Google's%20and%20OpenAI's%2C%20Bernstein's%20Mark%20Shmulik%20said%20Meta's%20aggressive%20push%20to%20overhaul%20itself%20into%20a%20top-to-bottom%20AI%20company%20could%20put%20it%20ahead%20of%20competitors%20and%20trigger%20a%20%26quot%3Bwave%20of%20panic%26quot%3B%20as%20competitors%20scramble%20to%20copy%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20is%20pouring%20hundreds%20of%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ebillions%20of%20dollars%20into%20building%20out%20AI%20data%20centers%20and%20luring%20talent%20to%20shore%20up%20its%20AI%20research%20teams.%20Last%20week%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-weighing-major-layoffs-as-it-pours-billions-into-ai-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20company%20was%20weighing%20up%20layoffs%2C%20with%20some%20managers%20being%20asked%20to%20draw%20up%20cost-cutting%20plans.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBernstein's%20Shmulik%20said%20this%20could%20be%20a%20signal%20that%20Meta%20is%20winning%20on%20a%20crucial%20front%20in%20the%20AI%20wars.%20While%20companies%20can%20win%20with%20world-class%20frontier%20models%2C%20they%20can%20also%20beat%20the%20competition%20by%20deploying%20AI%20so%20deeply%20across%20the%20core%20business%20that%20their%20competitive%20moat%20%26quot%3Bwidens%20beyond%20dispute%2C%26quot%3B%20Shmulik%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMeta%20has%20already%20demonstrated%20the%20compelling%20returns%20they're%20seeing%20from%20deploying%20AI%20to%20core%20workloads%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20Shmulik.%20%26quot%3BBut%20if%20the%20company%20can%20now%20re-design%20their%20operations%20from%20the%20ground%20up%20to%20be%20AI-forward%2C%20their%20potential%20cost%20and%20performance%20advantage%20could%20be%20insurmountable.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20one%20metric%2C%20Zuckerberg's%20efficiency%20drive%20over%20the%20past%20three%20years%20has%20paid%20off.%20Revenue%20per%20employee%20has%20steadily%20increased%20over%20that%20time%20period%2C%20with%20the%20company%20overtaking%20Amazon%20last%20year%2C%20according%20to%20data%20shared%20in%20the%20Bernstein%20note%20this%20week.%20Pinterest%20was%20the%20only%20company%20with%20a%20higher%20ratio.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20same%20time%2C%20Meta's%20capex%20and%20R%26amp%3BD%20spend%20per%20employee%20have%20significantly%20outpaced%20rivals%2C%20according%20to%20the%20Bernstein%20report%2C%20which%20could%20point%20to%20a%20reason%20for%20the%20potential%20layoffs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EInvestors%20appeared%20to%20react%20positively%20to%20Meta%20weighing%20up%20further%20cuts%2C%20with%20the%20company's%20shares%20up%20about%202%25%20early%20Monday.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229d0d2144-acd7-4028-8fba-195dc0c88be0%5C%22%3EAI-washing%3F%20Maybe%20not.%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELike%20other%20Big%20Tech%20companies%2C%20Meta%20has%20moved%20quickly%20to%20chase%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20has%20also%20been%20aggressively%20driving%20AI%20adoption%20internally.%20The%20company%20said%20it%20would%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-ai-employee-performance-review-overhaul-2025-11%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Estart%20grading%20employees%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20their%20%26quot%3BAI-driven%20impact%26quot%3B%20in%20performance%20reviews%20starting%20this%20year%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmeta-tracks-employees-ai-use-creates-game-to-boost-adoption-2025-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eand%20has%20tracked%3C%2Fa%3E%20how%20some%20teams%20have%20been%20using%20the%20tools%2C%20Business%20Insider%20previously%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECompanies%20including%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fatlassian-layoff-global-workforce-attributes-it-to-the-ai-era-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EAtlassian%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fceo-jack-dorsey-ai-impact-as-block-cuts-layoffs-workforce-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EBlock%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20cited%20AI%20as%20a%20reason%20for%20recent%20layoffs%2C%20raising%20the%20question%20of%20whether%20some%20leaders%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsam-altman-ai-washing-layoffs-job-cuts-openai-india-summit-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3BAI-washing%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20using%20the%20technology%20to%20camouflage%20other%20reasons%20for%20cuts%2C%20such%20as%20financial%20problems%20or%20overhiring%20during%20the%20COVID%20pandemic.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBernstein's%20Shmulik%20said%20that%20while%20AI-washing%20was%20possible%20in%20Meta%20and%20other%20companies'%20cases%2C%20he%20said%20that%20layoffs%20could%20now%20be%20seen%20as%20evidence%20that%20the%20company%20is%20seeing%20efficiency%20gains.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20company%20eliminated%20more%20than%2020%2C000%20jobs%20in%20late%202022%20and%20early%202023%20as%20Zuckerberg%20declared%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmark-zuckerberg-year-of-efficiency-working-meta-ai-2023-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E%26quot%3Byear%20of%20efficiency%2C%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20cutting%20non-technical%20roles%2C%20flattening%20management%20layers%2C%20and%20lifting%20what%20had%20been%20a%20sagging%20share%20price.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20Meta%20repeats%20a%20similar%20cycle%20for%20the%20AI%20era%2C%20it%20could%20set%20the%20mold%20for%20what%20a%20truly%20AI-first%20company%20could%20look%20like%2C%20Shmulik%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20one%20major%20player%20is%20able%20to%20redraw%20the%20blueprint%20for%20an%20AI-enabled%20organization%2C%20others%20will%20rush%20to%20replicate%20it...%20and%20we%20wonder%20if%20this%20could%20trigger%20a%20cascade%20of%20hurried%20pivots%2C%20half-formed%20strategies%2C%20and%20reactive%20restructuring%20across%20the%20ecosystem%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EHave%20something%20to%20share%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%20email%20at%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22mailto%3Ahlangley%40businessinsider.com%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ehlangley%40businessinsider.com%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20or%20Signal%20at%20628-228-1836.%20Use%20a%20personal%20email%20address%20and%20a%20non-work%20device%3B%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsider-guide-to-securely-sharing-whistleblower-information-about-powerful-institutions-2021-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_self%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cu%3Ehere's%20our%20guide%20to%20sharing%20information%20securely%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%