%2Fdonald-trump-osama-bin-laden-9-11-trump-says-he-predicted-9-11-a-year-before-it-happened-heres-the-truth-11224599%23publisher%3Dnewsstand%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22One%20Ukrainian%20operation%20holds%20some%20of%20the%20most%20important%20lessons%20for%20the%20West%20as%20it%20readies%20for%20future%20drone%20wars%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20still%20from%20video%20footage%20shows%20a%20firey%20explosion%20beside%20a%20grey%20jet%20on%20an%20airfield%20with%20'Failsafe'%20written%20in%20capital%20red%20letters%20over%20the%20footage%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69a7316ad3e2f1aef369e905%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221189%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUkraine%20conducted%20a%20devastating%2C%20large-scale%2C%20and%20new%20type%20of%20drone%20attack%20on%20Russian%20military%20bombers%20in%20Siberia.%3Cp%3EX%2FServiceSsu%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWestern%20militaries%20need%20to%20study%20one%20Ukrainian%20operation%20in%20particular%20for%20drone%20warfare%20lessons.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOfficials%20say%20Operation%20Spiderweb%2C%20which%20struck%20dozens%20of%20Russian%20jets%2C%20offers%20key%20lessons.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThe%20US%20Army's%20drone%20course%20director%20told%20Business%20Insider%20it's%20%26quot%3Bthe%20one%20event%20that%20I%20teach%20to%20the%20students.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EWestern%20militaries%20are%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-army-borrowing-from-ukraines-diy-drone-warfare-strategy-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Einvesting%20heavily%20in%20drone%20warfare%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20seeing%20their%20impact%20in%20Ukraine's%20fight%20against%20Russia's%20invasion.%20And%20while%20it%20isn't%20necessary%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwest-not-all-in-on-drones-maybe-right-call-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eabsorb%20every%20lesson%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20current%20and%20former%20military%20officials%20say%20one%20major%20operation%20is%20worth%20studying%20closely.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaj.%20Rachel%20Martin%2C%20director%20of%20the%20US%20Army's%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-army-mastering-drone-warfare-doesnt-mean-always-right-weapon-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3EUnmanned%20Advanced%20Lethality%20Course%3C%2Fa%3E%20designed%20to%20accelerate%20training%20on%20small%20drone%20warfare%2C%20told%20Business%20Insider%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraines-spiderweb-drone-attack-wake-up-call-us-in-pacific-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3E2025%20Operation%20Spiderweb%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20%26quot%3Bthe%20one%20event%20that%20I%20teach%20to%20the%20students.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%22442d73b2-b872-44bc-af2a-79bfc368c780%5C%22%3EOffensive%20potential%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20operation%2C%20Ukraine%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Foperation-spiderweb-5-ways-ukraine-drone-attack-new-era-warfare-2025-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Esmuggled%20drones%20into%20Russia%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20drove%20them%20to%20positions%20close%20to%20Russian%20airfields%2C%20and%20launched%20them%20at%20strategically%20valuable%20aircraft.%20The%20Ukrainian%20drones%20hit%2041%20Russian%20warplanes%20and%20caused%20an%20estimated%20%247%20billion%20in%20damage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20strikes%20showed%20how%20arsenals%20of%20small%2C%20cheap%20drones%20can%20destroy%20high-value%20military%20assets%20far%20from%20the%20front%20%E2%80%94%20and%20how%20difficult%20they%20are%20to%20defend%20against.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Aerial%20footage%20of%20a%20large%20grey%20aircraft%20on%20tarmac%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b816c5a7a4f9df67ba62fd%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221078%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EUkraine%20released%20videos%20of%20its%20drones%20targeting%20and%20hitting%20Russian%20military%20aircraft.%3Cp%3EX%2FDefenseU%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20operation%20was%20complex%20and%20took%20roughly%20a%20year%20and%20a%20half%20of%20planning%2C%20but%2C%20Martin%20said%2C%20it%20showed%20%26quot%3Bthat%20a%20small%20amount%20of%20money%20could%20be%20spent%20to%20destroy%20something%20at%20the%20strategic%20level%2C%26quot%3B%20in%20this%20case%2C%20bombers%20and%20other%20high-dollar%20aircraft.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20cost%20Russia%20billions%20of%20dollars%20when%20it%20%26quot%3Bis%20already%20hurting%20financially%20from%20being%20in%20a%20prolonged%20war.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESeeing%20that%20kind%20of%20low-cost%20attack%20destroying%20assets%20that%20could%20take%20years%20to%20replace%2C%20she%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bwas%20a%20big%20eye-opening%20experience%20for%20the%20world.%26quot%3B%20It%20highlighted%20not%20only%20what%20was%20possible%20with%20attack%20drones%20on%20offense%2C%20but%20also%20critical%20vulnerabilities.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%229cd3396c-ebaf-4e02-b6ed-53b490bcac45%5C%22%3EDefensive%20realizations%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Ukrainian%20operation%20sparked%20a%20realization%20in%20the%20West%20about%20the%20need%20for%20significantly%20more%20protection%20at%20air%20bases%2C%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eespecially%20those%20hosting%20essential%20mission%20tools%2C%20such%20as%20nuclear%20deterrence%20elements.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELt.%20Gen.%20Andrew%20Gebara%2C%20the%20deputy%20chief%20of%20staff%20for%20strategic%20deterrence%20and%20nuclear%20integration%20for%20the%20US%20Air%20Force%2C%20said%20of%20the%20operation%20last%20year%20that%20%26quot%3Bdisruptive%26quot%3B%20technologies%20like%20the%20drones%20seen%20in%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20%26quot%3Bwill%20have%20big%20implications%20not%20just%20for%20our%20bomber%20force%20or%20our%20nuclear%20force%20but%20really%20any%20critical%20infrastructure.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-air-force-taking-notes-from-ukraines-operation-spiderweb-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Ecounter-drone%20capabilities%3C%2Fa%3E%20at%20these%20bases.%20Do%20we%20need%20to%20continue%20to%20modernize%3F%20Do%20we%20need%20to%20accelerate%3F%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BYeah%2C%20absolutely%2C%20all%20that.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20majority%20of%20the%20most%20strategic%20US%20air%20assets%20are%20based%20inside%20the%20continental%20US.%20American%20airpower%20also%20depends%20heavily%20on%20warplanes%20stationed%20at%20air%20bases%20around%20the%20world.%20Defending%20against%20drones%20has%20proven%20challenging%20at%20both%20home%20and%20abroad%2C%20as%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsoldiers-confused-at-tower-22-before-drone-attack-killed-americans-2025-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3ETower%2022%20disaster%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20a%20number%20of%20domestic%20incidents%20have%20highlighted.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20satellite%20image%20shows%20multiple%20planes%20sitting%20at%20a%20base%20and%20large%20black%20scorch%20marks%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b815434d65ec51752a0e97%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221168%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EA%20satellite%20view%20shows%20military%20aircraft%2C%20some%20sitting%20destroyed%2C%20at%20the%20Belaya%20air%20base%2C%20near%20Stepnoy%2C%20Irkutsk%20region%2C%20Russia%2C%20after%20Ukraine's%20Operation%20Spiderweb.%3Cp%3E2025%20Planet%20Labs%20PBC%2Fvia%20REUTERS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EEuropean%20air%20bases%20have%20likewise%20grappled%20with%20the%20challenge%20of%20drones%2C%20making%20the%20lessons%20of%20Operation%20Spiderweb%20particularly%20poignant.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERetired%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EAir%20Marshal%20Greg%20Bagwell%2C%20who%20spent%2036%20years%20in%20the%20British%20Royal%20Air%20Force%20and%20served%20as%20its%20director%20of%20joint%20warfare%2C%20said%20last%20month%20that%20Operation%20Spiderweb%20holds%20key%20lessons%20that%20NATO%20allies%20need%20to%20learn.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20it%20comes%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-air-force-taking-notes-from-ukraines-operation-spiderweb-2025-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Emodern%20drone%20warfare%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20West%20has%20more%20to%20learn%20from%20operations%20like%20Spiderweb%20than%20from%20day-to-day%20front-line%20drone%20fighting%2C%20he%20said%20at%20the%20UK%20think%20tank%20Chatham%20House.%20The%20West%20doesn't%20necessarily%20need%20to%20engage%20in%20heavy%20quadcopter%20warfare%20at%20the%20front%20when%20it%20has%20artillery%20and%20substantial%20airpower.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20lessons%20that%20we%20need%20to%20learn%20are%20more%20from%20Operation%20Spiderweb%2C%20where%20Ukraine%20employed%20these%20drones%20in%20a%20much%20more%20sophisticated%20way%20and%20really%20did%20start%20to%20take%20out%20some%20significant%20targets%2C%26quot%3B%20Bagwell%20said.%20That%20operation%20had%20a%20high-level%20strategic%20effect%20on%20a%20stronger%20adversary%20for%20a%20comparatively%20lower%20cost.%20It's%20asymmetric%20warfare%20that%20the%20West%20can't%20ignore.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%20data-toc-id%3D%5C%227a977f94-ee13-4891-8a04-0b3e3695d569%5C%22%3EPicking%20up%20lessons%20from%20the%20war%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20is%20using%20drone%20warfare%20in%20ways%20beyond%20what%20Spiderweb%20demonstrated%2C%20drawing%20on%20other%20lessons%20from%20the%20war.%20In%20its%20war%20with%20Iran%20that%20started%20last%20month%2C%20it%20has%20used%20drones%20to%20attack%20Iranian%20targets%2C%20including%20the%20new%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-us-military-force-used-cheap-attack-drones-first-time-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eone-way%20attack%20LUCAS%20drones%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20also%20still%20employing%20traditional%20drone%20tactics%2C%20using%20platforms%20like%20the%20uncrewed%20strike%20and%20reconnaissance%20drone%20MQ-9%20Reaper.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Army's%20new%20drone%20course%20is%20just%20one%20of%20the%20many%20ways%20that%20it%20is%20advancing%20its%20drone%20warfare%20capabilities%2C%20along%20with%20other%20moves%20like%20plans%20to%20buy%20at%20least%20a%20million%20drones%20in%20the%20next%20two%20or%20so%20years.%20Allies%20across%20NATO%20are%20taking%20similar%20steps.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMartin%20said%20their%20power%20is%20undeniable%2C%20and%20the%20course%20itself%20was%20created%20because%20the%20Army%20could%20see%20that%20it%20was%20behind%20in%20small%20drone%20warfare%20and%20needed%20to%20fix%20that.%20But%20the%20US%20is%20not%20in%20the%20same%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fukraine-war-teaching-nato-air-forces-lessons-fighting-russia-2024-7%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Eexistential%20fight%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20Ukraine%20is%2C%20nor%20is%20it%20facing%20the%20same%20weapons%20shortages.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDrones%20have%20kept%20Ukraine%20in%20the%20fight%20against%20Russia%20even%20as%20other%20weapons%20ran%20out.%20They%20haven't%20been%20decisive%2C%20though%2C%20indicating%20that%20deep%20stocks%20of%20traditional%20and%20advanced%20weaponry%20still%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20Army%20course%20teaches%20soldiers%20that%20drones%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-army-mastering-drone-warfare-doesnt-mean-always-right-weapon-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22%5C%22%3Earen't%20always%20the%20right%20weapon%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBagwell%20also%20cautioned%20against%20leaning%20too%20heavily%20on%20drones.%20He%20said%20that%20drones%20have%20been%20%26quot%3Bhugely%20useful%26quot%3B%20for%20Ukraine%2C%20but%20%26quot%3Bthese%20have%20not%20won%20the%20war%20for%20either%20side.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20Ukraine%20has%20%26quot%3Bhad%20to%20adapt%20and%20fight%20the%20way%20they%20can%20only%20fight%2C%20and%20I%20applaud%20them%20for%20what%20they%20have%20done.%20But%20there%20is%20a%20question%20for%20us%20in%20the%20West%20as%20to%20whether%20that%20is%20the%20way%20we%20want%20to%20fight.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fone-ukraine-operation-shows-drone-lessons-western-militaries-need-2026-3%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773680463000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F69b7d09d4d65ec51752a0b44%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fone-ukraine-operation-shows-drone-lessons-western-militaries-need-2026-3%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Operation%20Spiderweb%20used%20drones%20to%20destroy%20billions%20of%20dollars'%20worth%20of%20Russian%20aircraft.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22sbaker%40insider.com%20(Sin%C3%A9ad%20Baker)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fone-ukraine-operation-shows-drone-lessons-western-militaries-need-2026-3%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BIn%20The%20Name%20Of%20God%26quot%3B%3A%20Khamenei's%20Aide's%20Letter%20To%20%26quot%3BMuslims%20Of%20The%20World%26quot%3B%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22Ali%20Larijani%2C%20the%20Secretary%20of%20Iran's%20Supreme%20National%20Security%20Council%2C%20has%20written%20a%20letter%20to%20%26quot%3BMuslims%20of%20the%20world%26quot%3B%20in%20what%20was%20seen%20as%20part%20rebuke%2C%20part%20theological%20indictment%2C%20and%20part%20strategic%20appeal.%22%2C%22published%22%3A1773680213000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2026-03%2F4nc2pt8_iran-air-plane-destroyed_650x400_03_March_26.jpg%3Fim%3DFeatu