as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhy-you-must-be-13-facebook-instagram-problematic-law-coppa-2022-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esimilar%20requirement%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoltbook%20added%20a%20series%20of%20disclaimers%20to%20the%20terms.%20Among%20the%20list%20is%20a%20statement%20advising%20against%20reliance%20on%20AI%20for%20information%20or%20decision-making.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMoltbook%20does%20not%20guarantee%20the%20accuracy%2C%20completeness%2C%20or%20reliability%26quot%3B%20of%20AI-generated%20content%2C%20the%20terms%20read.%20Users%20agree%20not%20to%20use%20the%20content%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bsubstitute%20for%20its%20own%20independent%20determinations.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeta%20acquired%20Moltbook%20in%20March%2C%20adding%20creators%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmoltbook-creator-sees-future-where-every-human-has-ai-bot-2026-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EMatt%20Schlicht%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20Ben%20Parr%20to%20the%20team%20of%20Meta's%20Superintelligence%20Lab.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20the%20acquisition%2C%20Moltbook%20had%20five%20rules%20in%20its%20terms%20of%20service.%20The%20ownership%20clause%20placed%20less%20liability%20on%20the%20human%20operator.%20%26quot%3BAI%20agents%20are%20responsible%20for%20the%20content%20they%20post%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20old%20rule%20said.%20%26quot%3BHuman%20owners%20are%20responsible%20for%20monitoring%20and%20managing%20their%20agents'%20behavior.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMoltbook%20was%20born%20from%20a%20meme%20moment%20on%20X%20about%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchina-openclaw-lobster-craze-uninstall-ai-agent-paid-side-hustle-2026-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAI%20agent%20OpenClaw%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20previously%20called%20Moltbot.%20Operators%20had%20to%20sign%20up%20with%20their%20X%20accounts.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20after%20the%20Meta%20acquisition%2C%20that%20hasn'